cer%20was%20in%20tremendous%20form%20as%20he%20dismissed%20the%20dangerous%20duo%20of%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20before%20coming%20back%20for%20his%20second%20spell%20and%20taking%20the%20wickets%20of%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya.%20After%20the%20innings%2C%20Shaheen%20was%20asked%20about%20his%20favourite%20wicket%20and%20although%20he%20said%20that%20both%20Rohit%20and%20Virat's%20wickets%20were%20crucial%2C%20he%20ended%20up%20choosing%20the%20dismissal%20of%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20skipper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20our%20plan%20with%20the%20new%20ball.%20I%20think%20both%20(Virat%20and%20Rohit)%20were%20crucial%20wickets%2C%20every%20batter%20is%20the%20same%20for%20me.%20But%20I%20think%20I%20liked%20Rohit's%20wicket%20better.%20The%20plans%20by%20our%20fast%20bowlers%20worked.%20Naseem%20is%20bowling%20at%20150%20kph%2C%20really%20happy%20with%20that%2C%20he's%20really%20fast.%20The%20new%20ball%20might%20swing%20and%20seam%2C%20but%20nothing%20much%20after%20that.%20It%20will%20be%20easier%20to%20score%20runs%20once%20the%20ball%20gets%20old%20(in%20the%20run%20chase)%2C%26quot%3B%20Shaheen%20Shah%20Afridi%20said%20during%20a%20post-innings%20presentation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20high-octave%20match%2C%20Ishan%20Kishan's%20unbridled%2082%20and%20Hardik%20Pandya's%20blinding%20batting%20display%20at%20Pallekele%20helped%20India%20post%20266%20after%20Pakistan's%20pacer%20attack%20dismantled%20Men%20in%20Blue's%20top%20order%20in%20their%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20campaign%20opener%20here%20at%20Pallekele%20International%20Cricket%20Stadium%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishan%20and%20Pandya's%20stand%20of%20138%20off%20140%20balls%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20India's%20total%20of%20266.%20Pakistan's%20pace%20attack%20was%20too%20good%20for%20the%20Indian%20batter%20as%20they%20bundled%20out%20Men%20in%20Blue%20for%20266%20in%2048.5%20overs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Paki