rch%20activity%20and%20engagement%2C%20and%20so%20on)%20to%20recommend%20potential%20jobs%20for%20you%2C%20to%20share%20with%20potential%20employers%20when%20you%20apply%20for%20a%20job%2C%20to%20enable%20employers%20to%20find%20potential%20candidates%2C%20and%20to%20show%20you%20more%20relevant%20advertising%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20updated%20privacy%20policy%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20microblogging%20platform%20does%20not%20define%20''biometric''%20in%20its%20policy%2C%20but%20the%20term%20generally%20refers%20to%20automated%20technologies%2C%20including%20facial%20recognition%20software%2C%20fingerprint%20taking%2C%20and%20palm%20and%20iris%20scanning%2C%20used%20for%20authenticating%20and%20verifying%20unique%20human%20body%20characteristics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20back%2C%20X%20introduced%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musks-x-introduces-job-listing-feature-for-verified-users-4333044%5C%22%3Efeature%20to%20post%20job%20listings%20for%20verified%20organizations%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20the%20microblogging%20platform.%C2%A0%20These%20moves%20come%20as%20Elon%20Musk%20is%20focused%20on%20making%20X%20an%20''everything%20app.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693709760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F9kac2es_twitter-x-650_650x400_24_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fx-plans-to-collect-users-biometric-data-along-with-education-and-job-history-report-4354712%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20of%20now%2C%20biometrics%20are%20for%20premium%20users%20and%20they%20will%20be%20given%20an%20option%20to%20submit%20their%20government%20ID%20and%20an%20image%20in%20order%20to%20add%20a%20verification%20layer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fx-plans-to-collect-users-biometric-data-along-with-education-and-job-history-report-4354712%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3