A00%20pm%20(0900%20GMT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchools%20and%20offices%20around%20the%20southern%20and%20eastern%20parts%20of%20the%20island%20were%20closed%20Sunday%2C%20and%20more%20than%20200%20domestic%20flights%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaikui%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20the%20first%20typhoon%20to%20make%20landfall%20in%20Taiwan%20in%20four%20years%26quot%3B%2C%20Taiwanese%20President%20Tsai%20Ing-wen%20said%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remind%20the%20people%20to%20make%20preparations%20for%20the%20typhoon%20and%20watch%20out%20for%20your%20safety%2C%20avoid%20going%20out%20or%20any%20dangerous%20activities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20storm%20was%20around%20180%20kilometres%20(110%20miles)%20east%20of%20Taiwan%20just%20before%209%3A00%20am%2C%20Taiwan's%20Central%20Weather%20Bureau%20said%20in%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20gathered%20some%20strength%20since%20yesterday%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20deputy%20director%20Fong%20Chin-tzu%2C%20urging%20to%20public%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bon%20guard%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20expected%20to%20pose%20a%20considerable%20threat%20to%20most%20areas%20in%20Taiwan%20with%20winds%2C%20rains%20and%20waves%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20storm%20would%20move%20west%20to%20the%20Taiwan%20Strait%20by%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Interior%20Ministry%20said%20authorities%20had%20evacuated%20more%20than%202%2C800%20people%20across%20seven%20cities%20in%20Taiwan%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20them%20from%20the%20mountainous%20county%20of%20Hualien%2C%20which%20neighbours%20Taitung.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20streets%20of%20Hualien%20were%20deserted%20Sunday%20morning%2C%20battered%20by%20unrelenting%20torrential%20rain%20under%20dark%20skies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20military%20has%20mobilised%20soldiers%20and%20equipment%20--%20such%20as%20amphibious%20vehicles%20and%20inflatable%20rubber%20boats%20--%20around%20the%20parts%20of%20Taiwan%20where%20Haikui%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20the%20heaviest%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20major%20storm%20to%20hit%20Taiwan%20was%20Typhoon%20Bailu%20in%202019%2C%20which%20left%20one%20person%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaikui%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20less%20severe%20than%20Saola%2C%20which%20bypassed%20Taiwan%20but%20triggered%20the%20highest%20threat%20level%20in%20nearby%20Hong%20Kong%20and%20southern%20China%20before%20it%20weakened%20into%20a%20tropical%20storm%20by%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693707600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Favmjs4jc_typhoon-generic_625x300_03_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthousands-evacuated-as-typhoon-haikui-heads-for-taiwan-4354705%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nearly%203%2C000%20people%20were%20evacuated%20from%20high-risk%20areas%20in%20eastern%20Taiwan%20ahead%20of%20Typhoon%20Haikui%20as%20authorities%20prepared%20Sunday%20for%20the%20first%20tropical%20storm%20to%20directly%20hit%20the%20island%20in%20four%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthousands-evacuated-as-typhoon-haikui-heads-for-taiwan-4354705%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%3A%20Key%20Issues%20To%20Keep%20An%20Eye%20On%20G20%20Summit%202023%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20just%20days%20to%20go%20for%20the%20G20%20Summit%2C%20India%20is%20gearing%20up%20to%20welcome%20a%20galaxy%20of%20powerful%20global%20leaders.%20Given%20the%20high-profile%20nature%20of%20the%20event%2C%20expectations%20are%20high.%20Important%20questions%20are%20also%20being%20raised.%20Will%20Xi%20Jinping%20give%20the%20event%20a%20miss%3F%20Would%20tensions%20over%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20War%20hijack%20the%20summit%3F%20Will%20Xi%20Jinping%20and%20Joe%20Biden%20have%20a%20bilateral%20meeting%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20summit%3F%20These%20issues%20will%20remain%20points%20of%20discussion%20over%20the%20next%20few%20days.%20Besides%20these%20questions%2C%20there%20are%20three%20broader%20issues%20that%20will%20attract%20significant%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20address%20the%20elephant%20in%20the%20room%20-%20Russia's%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%20Ever%20since%20the%20war%20began%20in%20February%202022%2C%20tensions%20have%20been%20high%20between%20Russia%20and%20NATO%20member%20states.%20During%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20Bali%20last%20year%2C%20these%20tensions%20threatened%20to%20overshadow%20the%20entire%20summit.%20Western%20powers%20pushed%20for%20a%20resolution%20that%20condemned%20Russian%20military%20action%20in%20Ukraine.%20During%20the%20Bali%20summit%2C%20Russian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Sergei%20Lavrov%20accused%20NATO%20countries%20of%20launching%20a%20%26quot%3Bhybrid%26quot%3B%20war%20and%20asked%20western%20powers%20not%20to%20%26quot%3Bpoliticise%26quot%3B%20the%20summit.%20Ukrainian%20President%20Vlodoymyr%20Zelenskiy%20participated%20virtually%2C%20addressing%20the%20summit%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20continues%20to%20dominate%20the%20international%20discourse.%20At%20a%20media%20interaction%2C%20Russian%20Ambassador%20to%20India%20Denis%20Alipov%20accused%20%26quot%3Bcertain%20countries%26quot%3B%20of%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bhijack%26quot%3B%20the%20G20%20Summit's%20agenda.%20Sergei%20Lavrov%20has%20also%20threatened%20to%20block%20any%20resolution%20that%20does%20not%20take%20into%20account%20Russian%20interests%20in%20Ukraine.%20As%20the%20host%2C%20the%20ball%20will%20be%20in%20India's%20court%20to%20ensure%20these%20tensions%20do%20not%20overshadow%20the%20meeting.%20The%20summit%20also%20provides%20India%20an%20opportunity%20to%20try%20and%20get%20both%20sides%20to%20reach%20some%20a%20middle%20ground.%20Given%20India's%20equations%20with%20both%20the%20NATO%20powers%20and%20Russia%2C%20this%20can%20be%20a%20possibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22bt7ilm4g%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fbt7ilm4g_delhi-g20-1200_625x300_25_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20geopolitical%20equations%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20have%20evolved%20significantly%20since%20the%20last%20G20%20Summit%20in%20Bali.%20While%20the%20US%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20remain%20close%20allies%2C%20tensions%20have%20arisen%20between%20the%20two%20regarding%20oil%20production.%20In%20July%2C%20OPEC%2B%20countries%20jointly%20agreed%20to%20cut%20down%20oil%20production%20by%20around%201.4%20million%20barrels%20per%20day.%20This%20fuelled%20fears%20of%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20oil%20prices.%20With%20western%20economies%20in%20particular%20struggling%20to%20control%20rising%20inflation%2C%20this%20came%20as%20a%20major%20setback.%20President%20Biden%20described%20this%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbetrayal%26quot%3B%20and%20vowed%20further%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20days%20have%20also%20seen%20a%20steady%20thaw%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia-Iran%20relations.%20Formerly%20bitter%20rivals%2C%20both%20sides%20have%20engaged%20in%20deepening%20dialogue%2C%20in%20an%20alleged%20deal%20brokered%20by%20the%20Chinese.%20For%20the%20US%2C%20which%20has%20long%20strained%20ties%20with%20Iran%2C%20this%20adds%20a%20layer%20of%20complication.%20The%20BRICS'%20resolution%20to%20induct%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Iran%2C%20Egypt%20and%20the%20UAE%20as%20new%20members%2C%20geopolitical%20equations%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20has%20changed%20significantly%20since%20the%20last%20G20%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20Biden%20use%20the%20G20%20Summit%20to%20iron%20out%20tensions%20with%20the%20US'%20Middle%20Eastern%20allies%3F%20With%20Saudi%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammad%20Bin%20Salman%2C%20Egyptian%20President%20Abdel%20Fattah%20el-Sisi%2C%20the%20UAE's%20President%20Mohamed%20Bin-Zayed%20and%20Oman's%20Sultan%20Haitham%20bin%20Tariq%20all%20slotted%20to%20attend%20the%20summit%2C%20this%20would%20be%20an%20important%20development%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20how%20will%20India%20use%20the%20G20%20to%20assert%20its%20position%20as%20an%20important%20global%20power%3F%20In%20a%20deeply%20divided%20international%20system%2C%20India%20is%20in%20a%20very%20unique%20position.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%20India-US%20ties%20have%20grown%20stronger.%20The%20US%20sees%20India%20as%20a%20vital%20strategic%20partner.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20India%20still%20maintains%20strong%20economic%20ties%20with%20Russia.%20Given%20the%20trust%20India%20enjoys%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20the%20summit%20offers%20a%20chance%20for%20India%20to%20emerge%20as%20a%20possible%20mediator.%20Its%20first%20challenge%20will%20be%20to%20ensure%20tensions%20between%20Russia%20and%20the%20West%20does%20not%20overshadow%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%224d0gqb2g%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F4d0gqb2g_delhi-traffic-police-g20-summit-ani_625x300_02_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coming%20few%20days%20offer%20India%20a%20chance%20to%20deepen%20its%20ties%20with%20the%20US.%20Since%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20in%20June%2C%20both%20sides%20have%20affirmed%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20relationship.%20Biden%20described%20the%20US'%20ties%20with%20India%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20defining%20partnership%20of%20the%2021st%20century%26quot%3B.%20The%20US%20President%20is%20set%20to%20reach%20India%20on%20September%207%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20hold%20bilateral%20discussions%20with%20PM%20Modi%20prior%20to%20the%20summit.%20The%20US%20clearly%20view