%20brother%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Lee%20Hsien%20Loong%2C%20for%20defamation%20over%20allegations%20relating%20to%20their%20rental%20of%20two%20state-owned%20bungalows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20conference%20will%20take%20place%20on%20Tuesday%20(September%205)%20at%209%20am%2C%20according%20to%20a%20hearing%20list%20on%20the%20Singapore%20Courts'%20website%2C%20Channel%20News%20Asia%20reported%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20ministers%20-%20Law%20and%20Home%20Affairs%20Minister%20K%20Shanmugam%20and%20Foreign%20Affairs%20Minister%20Vivian%20Balakrishnan%20-%20had%20sent%20lawyers'%20letters%20to%20Lee%20Hsien%20Yang%20in%20July%2C%20saying%20they%20would%20sue%20unless%20he%20apologises%2C%20withdraws%20his%20allegations%20and%20pays%20damages%20relating%20to%20the%20colonial-era%20bungalows%20in%20Ridout%20Road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20Facebook%20post%20on%20July%2027%2C%20Mr%20Shanmugam%20said%20Lee%20Hsien%20Yang%20had%20accused%20him%20and%20Mr%20Balakrishnan%20of%20%26quot%3Bacting%20corruptly%20and%20for%20personal%20gain%20by%20having%20Singapore%20Land%20Authority%20(SLA)%20give%20us%20preferential%20treatment%20by%20illegally%20felling%20trees%20without%20approval%2C%20and%20also%20having%20SLA%20pay%20for%20renovations%20to%2026%20and%2031%20Ridout%20Road%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20allegations%20are%20false%2C%20Mr%20Shanmugam%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELee%20Hsien%20Yang%20and%20his%20wife%20left%20the%20country%20after%20declining%20to%20attend%20a%20police%20interview%20in%20July%202022%20that%20relates%20to%20lying%20in%20judicial%20proceedings%20about%20the%20will%20of%20his%20late%20father%20and%20founding%20Prime%20Minister%20Lee%20Kuan%20Yew.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shanmugam%20says%20he%20rented%20Ridout%20Road%20property%20to%20prepare%20for%20sale%20of%20family%20home%2C%20not%20profiting%20from%20rental.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20surrounding%20the%20rental%20of%20the%20two%20Ridout%20Road%20state%20properties%20surfaced%20in%20early%20May%20when%20opposition%20politician%20and%20Reform%20Party%20chief%20Kenneth%20Jeyaretnam%20questioned%20if%20the%20ministers%20were%20%26quot%3Bpaying%20less%20than%20the%20fair%20market%20value%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20bungalows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Corrupt%20Practices%20Investigation%20Bureau%20(CPIB)%20was%20tasked%20to%20investigate%20whether%20there%20was%20any%20misconduct%20related%20to%20the%20transactions%20and%20found%20no%20wrongdoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPIB%20report%2C%20released%20on%20June%2028%2C%20said%20the%20two%20ministers%20did%20not%20benefit%20from%20getting%20any%20privileged%20information.%20They%20were%20not%20given%20preferential%20treatment%20and%20their%20rental%20rates%20were%20comparable%20to%20that%20of%20neighbouring%20properties%2C%20the%20report%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20was%20debated%20in%20parliament%20on%20July%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELee%20Hsien%20Yang%20has%20made%20at%20least%20eight%20Facebook%20posts%20on%20Ridout%20Road%20before%20and%20after%20CPIB's%20report%20and%20the%20parliament%20debate%2C%20according%20to%20the%20channel%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Facebook%20post%20on%20July%2023%20resulted%20in%20a%20correction%20direction%20under%20the%20Protection%20from%20Online%20Falsehoods%20and%20Manipulation%20Act%20(POFMA)%2C%20with%20the%20Law%20Ministry%20saying%20that%20it%20contained%20untrue%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Lee%20Hsien%20Yang%20had%20put%20up%20a%20correction%20notice%20as%20required%2C%20he%20also%20published%20a%20new%20post%20two%20days%20later%20saying%20he%20stood%20by%20what%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20his%20post%20was%20made%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Lee%20Hsien%20Yang%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20K%20Shanmugam%20and%20V%20Balakrishnan%20believe%20that%20they%20have%20a%20real%20case%2C%20then%20they%20should%20sue%20me%20in%20the%20UK.%26quot%3B%20Although%20Lee