t%20happy%20with%20the%20batting%20order%20at%20all.%20He%20indicated%20that%20India's%20seniors%20should%20bat%20at%20'tough%20positions.'%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20kind%20of%20form%20that%20Ishan%20Kishan%20is%20in%2C%20he%20scored%20half-century%20while%20opening%20in%20West%20Indies.%20The%20senior%20players%20should%20bat%20in%20the%20tough%20positions.%20Not%20any%20youngster.%20If%20someone%20is%20to%20bat%20at%20No.4%2C%20it%20should've%20been%20Virat%20Kohli%20or%20Rohit%20Sharma.%20The%20seniors%20should%20take%20up%20the%20difficult%20job.%20You%20should%20give%20a%20youngster%20his%20natural%20position%20to%20excel.%26quot%3B%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20said%20during%20commentary%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERain%20played%20spoilsport%20in%20the%20match.%20There%20were%20several%20rain%20delays%20as%20the%20second%20innings%20got%20washed%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishan%20(82%20off%2081%20balls)%20and%20Pandya%20(87%20off%2090%20balls)%20kept%20Pakistan%20bowlers%20at%20bay%20with%20a%20138-run%20fifth%20wicket%20stand%20of%20141%20balls.%20They%20joined%20forces%20after%20Pakistan%20pacers%20Afridi%2C%20who%20accounted%20for%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20early%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Haris%20Rauf%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112775-haris-rauf-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHaris%20Rauf%3C%2Fa%3E%20combined%20to%20reduce%20India%20to%2066%20for%204%20in%2014.1%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sense%2C%20it%20was%20a%20rather%20unfamiliar%20job%20for%20both%20Pandya%20and%20Kishan%2C%20who%20generally%20love%20to%20give%20a%20wallop%20to%20the%20bowlers.%20But%20the%20conditions%20at%20Pallekele%2C%20which%20always%20had%20a%20lick%20of%20drizzle%2C%20and%20a%20high-octane%20bowling%20attack%20meant%20that%20the%20Indian%20pair%20would%20have%20to%20curb%20their%20shot-making%20instincts.%20They%20had%20to%20be%20precise%20in%20the%20selection%20of%20each%20shot%2C%20and%2