ehicle%20lineup%2C%20ringing%20in%20a%20new%20stage%20in%20the%20fight%20to%20catch%20up%20to%20Tesla%20Inc.%20and%20defend%20sales%20in%20its%20most%20important%20market%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vision%20Neue%20Klasse%20concept%20car%2C%20on%20display%20at%20next%20week's%20IAA%20show%20in%20Munich%2C%20shows%20off%20BMW's%20dedicated%20EV%20underpinnings%20due%20in%202025%20-%20around%20the%20time%20Mercedes-Benz%20Group%20AG%20is%20introducing%20its%20new%20battery-powered%20models.%20Software%20issues%20have%20delayed%20similar%20architectures%20from%20Volkswagen%20AG%2C%20pushing%20back%20key%20Porsche%20and%20Audi%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20sleek%20coupe%2C%20BMW%20is%20veering%20away%20from%20a%20decades-old%20tradition%20of%20advertising%20mainly%20the%20performance%20of%20its%20'ultimate%20driving%20machines.'%20Instead%2C%20it's%20touting%20a%20digital%20display%20projected%20onto%20the%20entire%20width%20of%20the%20windscreen%20as%20well%20as%20software%20that%20can%20process%20voice%20commands%20and%20hand%20gestures.%20The%20move%20is%20a%20nod%20to%20customers%20in%20China%2C%20who%20are%20increasingly%20going%20for%20homegrown%20brands%20such%20as%20BYD%20Co.%20and%20Nio%20Inc.%20that%20have%20been%20better%20at%20building%20EVs%20with%20gadgets%20geared%20to%20local%20tastes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Neue%20Klasse%20%26quot%3Bsets%20our%20course%20for%20the%20next%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20Oliver%20Zipse%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBMW%2C%20Mercedes%20and%20Audi%20long%20dominated%20sales%20of%20premium%20combustion-engine%20cars%20in%20China%2C%20but%20have%20been%20caught%20on%20the%20back%20foot%20by%20the%20country's%20rapid%20shift%20to%20electric%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBYD%20this%20year%20dethroned%20VW%20as%20China's%20top-selling%20automaker%2C%20and%20Mercedes%20slashed%20prices%20for%20its%20flagship%20electric%20sedan%20there%20late%20last%20year%20after%20disappointing%20sales.%20Electric%20cars%20and%20plug-in%20hybrids%20are%20expected%20to%20make%20up%2090%25%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20auto%20market%20around%20the%20end%20of%20this%20decade%2C%20adding%20urgency%20for%20Western%20premium%20brands%20to%20accelerate%20their%20offerings.%20A%20price%20war%20in%20China%20started%20by%20Tesla%20has%20also%20upped%20the%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBMW%20is%20growing%20in%20China%2C%20especially%20on%20electric%20cars%2C%20and%20the%20carmaker%20isn't%20affected%20by%20the%20price%20war%20because%20of%20its%20positioning%20in%20the%20premium%20segment%2C%20Zipse%20told%20reporters%20on%20Saturday%20in%20Munich.%20The%20Neue%20Klasse%2C%20he%20added%2C%20will%20be%20even%20more%20profitable%20than%20the%20company's%20current%20lineup%20of%20battery-powered%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBMW's%20top-end%20Neue%20Klasse%20models%20will%20have%20a%20range%20of%20as%20much%20as%20800%20kilometers%20(497%20miles)%20and%20charge%20from%2010%25%20to%2080%25%20in%20under%20half%20an%20hour%2C%20numbers%20that%20likely%20won't%20make%20them%20best%20in%20class.%20Last%20year%2C%20an%20electric%20prototype%20from%20Mercedes%20drove%20more%20than%201%2C000%20kilometers%20on%20a%20single%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20BMW%20still%20ranks%20second%20in%20China%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20tech%20features%20in%20its%20cars%2C%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20consumer%20survey%20by%20consultancy%20AlixPartners.%20BMW%20came%20in%20behind%20Geely's%20Zeekr%20but%20ahead%20of%20Xpeng%2C%20Tesla%20and%20VW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20new%20focus%20on%20digital%20features%2C%20BMW%20won't%20entirely%20throw%20its%20brand%20traditions%20overboard.%20While%20most%20EVs%20these%20days%20offer%20swift%20acceleration%2C%20the%20Neue%20Klasse%20will%20be%20more%20fun%20to%20drive%20at%20higher%20speeds%20than%20many%20competitors%2C%20according%20to%20Zipse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20be