ents.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20central%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-ron-desantis-dont-say-gay-bill-law-2022-3%5C%22%3EFlorida%20lawmakers%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20they%20were%20considering%20%26quot%3Ball%20legislative%2C%20legal%20and%20executive%20options%20available%26quot%3B%20to%20stop%20business%20owners%20in%20a%20small%20town%20from%20voluntarily%20displaying%20rainbow%20decals%20in%20their%20windows%20indicating%20that%20they%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bsafe%20place%26quot%3B%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffight-over-floridas-dont-say-gay-bill-explained-2022-2%5C%22%3ELGBTQ%2B%20people%C2%A0who%20feel%20threatened%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20Republican%20lawmakers%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20officials%20in%20Mount%20Dora%20two%20weeks%20ago%20warning%20that%20the%20new%2C%20optional%20city-sponsored%20program%20could%20put%20the%20central%20Florida%20community%20outside%20Orlando%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20crosshairs%20of%20potentially%20detrimental%20and%20absolutely%20unnecessary%20economic%20harm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawmakers%20cited%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbud-light-transgender-controversy-backlash-boycotts-history%5C%22%3Eboycotts%20of%20Bud%20Light%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Target%2C%20which%20followed%20the%20brands'%20efforts%20to%20promote%20diversity%20and%20inclusion%20of%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMount%20Dora's%20city%20council%20approved%20the%20Safe%20Place%20Initiative%20last%20month.%20The%20city%20of%2017%2C000%20residents%20is%20known%20for%20its%20antique%20shops%20and%20weekend%20festivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mission%20of%20the%20Safe%20Place%20Initiative%20is%20to%20provide%20the%20community%20with%20easily%20accessible%20safety%20information%20and%20safe%20places%20throughout%20the%20city%20they%20can%20turn%20to%20if%20they%20are%20the%20victims%20of%20an%20anti-LGBTQ%2B%20or%20o