0Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20is%20also%20part%20of%20the%20committee%2C%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20pointed%20out%20that%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20%26quot%3Bhas%20been%20excluded%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20committee%2C%20and%20instead%20they%20took%20former%20Congress%20leader%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20deliberate%20insult%20to%20the%20system%20of%20parliamentary%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chowdhury%20said%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20members%20of%20the%20committee%20are%20former%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%20chairman%20NK%20Singh%2C%20former%20Lok%20Sabha%20Secretary%20General%20%C2%A0Subhash%20C%20Kashyap%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Harish%20Salve%2C%20and%20former%20Chief%20Vigilance%20Commissioner%20Sanjay%20Kothari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20will%20look%20into%20the%20feasibility%20of%20holding%20not%20only%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assembly%20elections%20simultaneously%2C%20but%20also%20elections%20to%20municipalities%20and%20panchayats%2C%20according%20to%20the%20gazette%20notification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20hesitation%20whatsoever%20in%20declining%20to%20serve%20on%20the%20committee%20whose%20terms%20of%20reference%20have%20been%20prepared%20in%20a%20manner%20to%20guarantee%20its%20conclusions.%20It%20is%2C%20I%20am%20afraid%2C%20a%20total%20eyewash.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20sudden%20attempt%20to%20thrust%20a%20constitutionally%20suspect%2C%20pragmatically%20non-feasible%20and%20logistically%20unimplementable%20idea%20on%20the%20nation%2C%20months%20before%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20raises%20serious%20concerns%20about%20ulterior%20motives%20of%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20leader%20said%20in%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFurthermore%2C%20I%20find%20that%20the%20current%20LOP%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20has%20been%20excluded.%20This%20is%20a%20deliberate%2