hardson%2C%20the%20former%20two-term%20New%20Mexico%20governor%20and%20veteran%20diplomat%2C%20has%20died%20at%2075.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERichardson%20served%20as%20ambassador%20to%20the%20UN%20and%20Energy%20Secretary%20under%20President%20Bill%20Clinton.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELast%20month%2C%20he%20was%20nominated%20for%20a%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%20over%20his%20work%20to%20free%20political%20prisoners.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBill%20Richardson%2C%20the%20former%20two-term%20New%20Mexico%20governor%20and%20US%20Ambassador%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20who%20just%20last%20month%20was%20nominated%20for%20a%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%20for%20his%20work%20to%20free%20political%20prisoners%2C%20died%20on%20Friday%20in%20his%20sleep%20at%20his%20summer%20home%20in%20Massachusetts.%20He%20was%2075.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Richardson%20Center%20for%20Global%20Engagement%20confirmed%20the%20veteran%20diplomat's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20lived%20his%20entire%20life%20in%20the%20service%20of%20others%20%E2%80%94%20including%20both%20his%20time%20in%20government%20and%20his%20subsequent%20career%20helping%20to%20free%20people%20held%20hostage%20or%20wrongfully%20detained%20abroad.%20There%20was%20no%20person%20that%20Governor%20Richardson%20would%20not%20speak%20with%20if%20it%20held%20the%20promise%20of%20returning%20a%20person%20to%20freedom%2C%26quot%3B%20Mickey%20Bergman%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20Richardson%20Center%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_DAFE8C6D-35A3-DAB5-D13F-56BCF0F6D250%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%20data-article-gutter%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20has%20lost%20a%20champion%20for%20those%20held%20unjustly%20abroad%20and%20I%20have%20lost%20a%20mentor%20and%20a%20dear%20friend%2C%26quot%3B%20Bergman%20add