media%E2%80%99s%20reportage%20of%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99%20also%20notes%20how%20certain%20media%20practices%20led%20to%20the%20vilification%20of%20the%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%20its%20recommendations%2C%20it%20noted%3A%20%E2%80%9CMeitei%20media%20became%20a%20party%20to%20the%20vili%20fication%20of%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20especially%20the%20Assam%20Rifles.%20It%20failed%20in%20its%20duty%20by%20constant%20propaganda%20against%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20claiming%20that%20it%20was%20only%20purveying%20the%20views%20of%20the%20public.%20It%20failed%20to%20verify%20the%20facts%2C%20weigh%20them%20and%20then%20use%20them%20in%20its%20reportage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20the%20state%20government%20also%20tacitly%20supported%20this%20vili%20cation%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-police-files-fir-against-assam-rifles-for-allowing-kuki-militants-to-flee%5C%22%3Eallowing%20Manipur%20Police%20to%20file%20an%20FIR%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20%E2%80%9Csuggesting%20that%20one%20hand%20of%20the%20state%20did%20not%20know%20what%20the%20other%20what%20the%20other%20was%20doing%20or%20this%20was%20deliberate%20action.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20between%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20paramilitary%20forces%2C%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20and%20Manipur%20police%20has%20been%20unprecedented.%20The%20Manipur%20Police%E2%80%99s%20FIR%20against%20it%20was%20ostensibly%20for%20%E2%80%9Callowing%20Kuki%20Militants%20to%20flee%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20The%20director%20general%20of%20Assam%20Rifles%2C%20Lt%20General%20P.C.%20Nair%2C%20on%20September%201%2C%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fassam-rifles-dg-manipur-situation-unprecedented%5C%22%3Ethat%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20was%20unprecedented.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInternet%20ban%20and%20bias%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20took%20a%20straightforward%20view%20of%20the%20role%20of%20the%20internet%20ban%20in%20affecting%20cross-checking%20and%20monitoring%20of%20news%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20straight%20%E2%80%9Cmistake%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20surefire%20way%20of%20allowing%20rumours%20to%20float.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternet%20was%20first%20cut%20off%20in%20the%20state%20on%20May%203.%20Several%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-government-extends-internet-shutdown-till-june-30%5C%22%3Eorders%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20since%20then%20called%20for%20its%20continuation%2C%20until%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-internet-restricted-access-mobile-suspended%5C%22%3Erestricted%20use%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20permitted%20in%20late%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20thanks%20to%20this%20breakdown%20of%20communication%2C%20journalists%20effectively%20had%20to%20follow%20the%20government%20narrative%2C%20which%20under%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20%E2%80%9Cbecame%20a%20narrow%20ethnic%20one%20playing%20up%20to%20the%20biases%20of%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCommunication%20blockade%20by%20the%20government%20had%20a%20deleterious%20effect%20on%20journalism%20as%20it%20directly%20impacted%20the%20ability%20of%20journalists%20to%20communicate%20with%20each%20other%2C%20their%20editors%20and%20their%20sources.%20It%20also%20affected%20the%20media%20because%20local%20news%20gathered%20without%20any%20communication%20links%20was%20not%20sufficient%20to%20give%20a%20balanced%20view%20of%20the%20situation%20and%20often%2C%20even%20that%20was%20not%20enough%20to%20fi%20ll%20their%20pages%20or%20meet%20their%20news%20requirement%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20an%20internet%20ban%20becomes%20absolutely%20necessary%2C%20the%20report%20said%2C%20then%20news%20platforms%20should%20be%20exempted%20from%20the%20ban%20and%20a%20committee%20comprising%20the%20media%20representatives%2C%20civil%20society%20organisations%20and%20government%20representatives%20should%20monitor%20the%20ban%20and%20its%20duration%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20no%20circumstances%20should%20the%20state%20government%20go%20against%20the%20guidelines%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EAnuradha%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EBhasin%3C%2Fem%3E%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20stressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20report%20said%20that%20during%20the%20conflict%2C%20Manipur%20media%20had%20effectively%20become%20Meitei%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMeitei%20media%2C%20for%20that%20is%20what%20Manipur%20media%20seemed%20to%20have%20become%20during%20the%20conflict%2C%20acted%20collectively%20with%20editors%20consulting%20each%20other%20and%20agreeing%20on%20a%20common%20narrative%20e.g.%2C%20agreeing%20on%20common%20language%20to%20report%20an%20incident%2C%20referring%20to%20certain%20use%20of%20language%20or%20even%20not%20reporting%20an%20event.%20This%20the%20EGI%20team%20was%20told%20was%20because%20they%20did%20not%20want%20to%20inflame%20the%20already%20volatile%20situation%20further.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20noted%20that%20this%20practice%20apparently%20originated%20from%20the%20days%20when%20insurgent%20groups%20were%20active%20in%20the%20Valley%20and%20threatened%20newspaper%20editors%20for%20any%20adverse%20reporting.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20downside%20of%20such%20an%20approach%20during%20ethnic%20violence%20is%20that%20it%20can%20easily%20slip%20into%20forging%20a%20common%20ethnic%20narrative%20and%20lead%20to%20a%20collective%20downslide%20of%20journalistic%20principles%20by%20deciding%20what%20to%20report%20and%20what%20to%20censor.%20This%20seems%20to%20have%20happened%20to%20some%20extent%20during%20the%20present%20cycle%20of%20ethnic%20violence%20between%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20Kukis%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20also%20said%20that%20there%20are%20%E2%80%9Cclear%20indications%20that%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20state%20became%20partisan%20during%20the%20conflict%2C%E2%80%9D%20highlighting%20it%20as%20a%20failure%20of%20performing%20its%20duty%20as%20a%20democratic%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20Meitei%20government%2C%20Meitei%20police%20and%20Meitei%20bureaucracy%20in%20Imphal%20and%20the%20tribal%20people%20living%20in%20the%20Hills%20have%20no%20faith%20in%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFind%20the%20full%20report%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F668684879%2FReport-of-the-fact-finding-mission-on-media-s-reportage-of-the-ethnic-violence-in-Manipur%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20Report%20of%20the%20fact-finding%20mission%20on%20media's%20reportage%20of%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EReport%20of%20the%20fact-finding%20mission%20on%20media%E2%80%99s%20reportage%20of%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fuser%2F286754081%2FThe-Wire%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20The%20Wire's%20profile%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Scribd%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F668684879%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-Lp8tCFRVSIoHyx3dwgnx%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%220.7080062794348508%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Report%20of%20the%20fact-finding%20mission%20on%20media's%20reportage%20of%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693668660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F25122407%2FF4M3tHNWUAAGBhf.jpeg%22%2C%