%20reporting%20of%20the%20events%20which%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20align%20with%20the%20official%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journalists%20also%20rued%20the%20labels%20of%20%E2%80%9Canti-nationals%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cterror%20sympathisers%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cpro-Pakistan%20reporters%E2%80%9D%20allegedly%20used%20by%20authorities%20against%20them%20while%20terming%20the%20action%20against%20the%20four%20incarcerated%20Kashmiri%20journalists%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwarning%E2%80%9D%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20report%20points%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fjk-admin-takes-control-of-kashmir-press-club%5C%22%3Eshutting%20down%20of%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20only%20press%20club%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20authorities%20and%20the%20sensational%20assassination%20of%20Shujaat%20Bukhari%2C%20senior%20journalist%20and%20editor%20who%20was%20shot%20dead%20outside%20his%20office%20in%202018%2C%20to%20underline%20the%20alleged%20deterioration%20of%20press%20freedom%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20journalists%20who%20spoke%20with%20the%20BBC%20also%20felt%20under%20threat%20from%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20its%20rebuttal%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20said%20that%20its%20%E2%80%9Cactions%E2%80%9D%20against%20journalists%20%E2%80%9Chave%20stood%20the%20test%20of%20law%20and%20judiciary%20and%20changed%20the%20security%20environment%20in%20the%20UT%20(Union%20territory)%20immensely%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20police%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20while%20falsely%20accusing%20the%20BBC%20of%20referring%20to%20J%26amp%3BK%20as%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20Occupied%20Kashmir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20article%2C%20which%20appeared%20on%20Friday%2C%20September%201%2C%20refers%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20as%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20administered%20Kashmir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BBC%20said%20it%20spoke%20with%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20journalists%2C%20%E2%80%9Cmore%20than%2090%20percent%E2%80%9D%20of%20whom%20claimed%20to%20have%20been%20summoned%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20some%20of%20them%20multiple%20times%20over%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20in%202019%20when%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20was%20bifurcated%20and%20downgraded%20into%20two%20union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisputing%20the%20report%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20said%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cmaintains%20the%20highest%20standards%20of%20professionalism%20and%20functions%20squarely%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20law%E2%80%9D.%20The%20BBC%20report%20uses%20%E2%80%9Cquotes%20of%20unidentified%20journalists%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20particulars%20of%20date%20and%20place%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbolster%20..%20non-existent%20claims%20of%20state%20overreach%20against%20journalists%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJ%26amp%3BK%20Police%20condemns%20the%20attempt%20of%20a%20media%20house%20such%20as%20the%20BBC%20to%20misrepresent%20the%20conditions%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20in%20which%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20has%20stood%20firmly%20on%20the%20front%20lines%20in%20the%20war%20against%20terror%20and%20lost%20thousands%20of%20its%20bravest%20men%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20safeguard%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20national%20and%20international%20media%20organisations%2C%20including%20the%20Paris-based%20press%20freedom%20watchdog%20Reporters%20Sans%20Frontiers%20(RSF)%20and%20the%20New%20York-headquartered%20Committee%20to%20Protect%20Journalists%2C%20have%20flagged%20the%20deterioration%20of%20press%20freedom%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20calling%20upon%20authorities%20to%20release%20the%20four%20journalists%20incarcerated%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20slipped%2011%20ranks%20further%20to%20161%20out%20of%20180%20countries%20in%20terms%20of