%5C%222120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Grocery%20store%20shopping%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e7c544a7adf70019078304%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWoman%20looking%20at%20prices%20during%20inflation%20while%20doing%20shopping%20in%20supermarket.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMarketers%20this%20year%20are%20expected%20to%20spend%20%24128%20billion%20on%20retail%20media.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20of%20this%20uptick%20is%20coming%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20traditional%20channels%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20trade%20budgets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Walmart%2C%20and%20Instacart%20are%20leading%20the%20way%20in%20retail%20media.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMarketers%20this%20year%20are%20expected%20to%20spend%20%24128%20billion%20on%20retail%20media%2C%20or%20advertising%20on%20ecommerce%20sites%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20global%20forecast%20from%20the%20marketing%20research%20firm%20WARC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetail%20media%20%E2%80%94%20which%20WARC%20forecasts%20to%20be%20up%2010.2%25%20over%20last%20year%20and%20to%20grow%20another%2010.5%25%20next%20year%20%E2%80%94%20appears%20to%20be%20coming%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20Google%20search%20and%20traditional%20offline%20media%20channels%20like%20linear%20TV%2C%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetail%20media%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20hottest%20categories%20in%20advertising%20in%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20partially%20due%20to%20marketers%20who%20are%20worried%20about%20the%20economy%20investing%20in%20ads%20that%20more%20directly%20drive%20purchases%2C%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlex%20Brownsell%2C%20WARC%20head%20of%20content%2C%20said%20some%20of%20this%20uptick%20is%20coming%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20traditional%20channels%2C%20such%20as%20linear%20TV%2C%20print%20newspapers%20and%20magazines%2C%20and%20audio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpend%20on%20linear%20TV%20is%20expected%20to%20drop%20by%205.4%25%20this%20year%2C%20bringing%20its%20share%20of%20total%20global%20ad%20dollars%20down%20to%2016.3%25%2C%20according%20to%20WARC.%20Ad%20budgets%20placed%20on%20%26quot%3Bnewsbrands%20and%20magazines%26quot%3B%20will%20fall%205.9%25%20and%20audio%20down%20by%200.8%25.%20Meanwhile%2C%20retail%20media%20is%20forecast%20to%20grow%20its%20share%20to%2013.3%25%20of%20total%20ad%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetail%20media%20players%20are%20also%20managing%20to%20capture%20some%20search%20spend%20that%20was%20ordinarily%20placed%20with%20Google%2C%20according%20to%20Bill%20Fisher%2C%20Insider%20Intelligence%20principal%20analyst.%20US%20search%20spend%20on%20retail%20media%20properties%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%2018.7%25%20this%20year%2C%20while%20search%20spend%20outside%20retail%20media%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20just%205%25%2C%20per%20Insider%20Intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20has%20careened%20back%20and%20forth%20over%20different%20shopping%20strategies%20and%20cycled%20through%20a%20handful%20of%20e-commerce%20leaders%20over%20the%20years%20as%20it%20sought%20to%20take%20on%20Amazon%20to%20become%20the%20first%20choice%20of%20shoppers.%20Despite%20offering%20Shopping%20Ads%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fservices.google.com%2Ffh%2Ffiles%2Fblogs%2Fbuilding_a_retail_media_business_with_google.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eanalytics%20and%20order%20management%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20tools%2C%20industry%20analysts%20usually%20don't%20consider%20Google%20as%20a%20retail%20media%20operator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20retail%20media%20surge%20include%20Amazon%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20account%20for%20more%20than%20a%20third%20(34.6%25)%20of%20global%20retail%20media%20spending%20in%202023%20and%20remains%20the%20incumbent%20and%20dominant%20player%20by%20far.%20It%20also%20includes%20supermarkets%20like%20Kroger%2C%20ecommerce%20sites%20like%20Farfetch%2C%20and%20apps%20like%20Uber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20all%20retail%20media%20spend%20is%20coming%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20Google%20and%20traditional%20advertising%20channels.%20Forrester's%20second-quarter%20marketing%20CMO%20pulse%20survey%20found%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20retail%20media%20spend%20is%20coming%20from%20existing%20trade%20and%20shopper%20marketing%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetailers%20are%20cannibalizing%20those%20budgets%20to%20fuel%20growth%20of%20their%20retail%20media%20networks%2C%20said%20Nikhil%20Lai%2C%20senior%20analyst%20at%20Forrester.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetail%20media%20sellers%20are%20aggressively%20going%20after%20a%20bigger%20cut%20of%20ad%20budgets%20by%20expanding%20their%20ad%20formats%20beyond%20search.%20Amazon%20has%20a%20range%20of%20video%2C%20streaming%2C%20and%20social%20commerce%20offerings.%20Walmart%20is%20expanding%20its%20in-store%20advertising%20business%2C%20bringing%20more%20ads%20to%20self-checkout%20screens%20and%20in-store%20audio.%20And%20Instacart%20detailed%20in%20its%20recent%20IPO%20filing%20that%20it%20intends%20to%20roll%20out%20%26quot%3Bshoppable%20products%20brand%20pages.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20every%20retail%20media%20network%20is%20set%20to%20become%20a%20big%20ad%20player.%20Insider%20Intelligence%20forecast%20in%20March%20that%20Instacart%20(42.8%25)%20and%20Walmart%20(39.1%25)%20will%20be%20the%20two%20fastest%20growing%20players%20in%20all%20of%20US%20digital%20advertising%20this%20year%2C%20ahead%20of%20non-retail%20media%20companies%20like%20Apple%20and%20TikTok.%20Amazon%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20by%2017.4%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForrester's%20Lai%20said%20that%20there's%20a%20long-tail%20of%20retail%20media%20networks%20that%20lack%20sufficient%20traffic%20on%20their%20sites%20and%20in%20their%20apps%20to%20earn%20the%20spending%20that%20the%20triopoly%20of%20Amazon%2C%20Walmart%2C%20Instacart%20generates%2C%20so%20they'll%20likely%20focus%20on%20letting%20ad