3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20them%20left%20without%20any%20money.%20Mang%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20us%20left%20in%20a%20hurry%2C%20so%20no%20one%20was%20able%20to%20take%20money.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20we%20will%20manage%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20My%20passport%20and%20Aadhaar%20are%20still%20at%20my%20place.%20I%20am%20fearing%20that%20sooner%20or%20later%2C%20our%20houses%20will%20also%20be%20burnt%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20roiled%20by%20ethnic%20violence%20since%20May%202%20%E2%80%93%20had%20been%20particularly%20tense%20since%20August%2029.%20As%20many%20as%20eight%20people%20have%20died%20since%20then%20individuals.%20Earlier%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported%20that%20a%20few%20families%20were%20still%20residing%20in%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20New%20Lambulane%2C%20with%20the%20police%20providing%20them%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20Lambulane%20area%20is%20tightly%20populated.%20Outside%20the%20area%2C%20many%20Central%20and%20state%20forces%20had%20been%20deployed%20to%20guard%20the%20Kuki%20families%20living%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20one%20of%20the%20Naga%20residents%20living%20in%20New%20Lambulane%2C%20who%20said%20later%20in%20the%20day%20on%20September%202%20that%C2%A0%20personnel%20of%20%E2%80%9CManipur%20Police%2C%20the%20CRPF%20and%20RAF%E2%80%9D%20were%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20place%20is%20still%20safe.%20I%E2%80%99m%20wondering%20why%20they%20had%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98forcefully%E2%80%99%20taken%20out%20from%20the%20area%2C%20especially%20at%202%3A30%20in%20the%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Naga%20resident%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20DGP%20Rajiv%20Singh%20but%20he%20refused%20to%20give%20a%20comment%20over%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2024%20evacuated%20people%20have%20w