at%20UC%20Riverside%20who%20has%20studied%20how%20modern%20AI%20models%20use%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20things%20that%20come%20carted%20along%20with%20this%2C%20not%20true%20information%20that%20sustainability%20and%20digital%20innovation%20go%20hand-in-hand%2C%20like%20'you%20can%20keep%20growing'%20and%20'everything%20can%20be%20scaled%20massively%2C%20and%20it's%20still%20fine'%20and%20that%20one%20type%20of%20technology%20fits%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20Russell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20momentum%20around%20AI%2C%20and%20its%20environmental%20footprint%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20grow%20as%20companies%20look%20to%20weave%20large%20language%20models%20into%20more%20of%20their%20operations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussell%20thinks%20a%20better%20approach%20would%20be%20to%20focus%20on%20other%20innovations%20that%20are%20more%20sustainable%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2F2014%2F01%2Fits-time-to-take-mesh-networks-seriously-and-not-just-for-the-reasons-you-think%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emesh%20networks%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scientificamerican.com%2Farticle%2Fhow-indigenous-groups-are-leading-the-way-on-data-privacy%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTo%2520shore%2520up%2520their%2520defenses%2Cwho%2520has%2520access%2520to%2520it.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eindigenous%20data%20privacy%20initiatives%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Communities%20are%20setting%20up%20data%20privacy%20controls%20and%20internet%20connectivity%20on%20their%20own%20terms%20and%20in%20ways%20that%20don't%20rely%20as%20much%20on%20big%20tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can%20pinpoint%20the%20examples%2C%20however%20small%2C%20of%20where%20people%20are%20actually%20designing%20technology%20that's%20sustainable%20then%20we%20can%20start%20to%20imagine%20and%20critique%20these%20huge%20technologies%20that%20aren't%20sustainable%20both%20environmentally%2