%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Things%20We%20Need%20to%20Do%20Before%20We%20Speak%20of%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F20123532%2FIMG_2186.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20revival%20in%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-knows-an-actual-ucc-will-be-an-electoral-disaster-for-him%5C%22%3Eprime%20minister%20himself%20weighing%20in%20on%20its%20necessity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20we%20need%20to%20be%20clear%20that%20this%20demand%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20its%20collaborators%20such%20as%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20and%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20is%20neither%20based%20on%20its%20mention%20in%20the%20constitution%E2%80%99s%20Directive%20Principles%20nor%20driven%20by%20altruistic%20intentions.%20Much%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Funveiling-indias-long-history-of-hypocrisy-on-cow-slaughter-laws%5C%22%3Equestion%20of%20cow%20protection%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20periodic%20revival%20of%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20targets%20the%20Muslims%20of%20India%3B%20a%20weapon%20to%20spread%20hatred%2C%20false%20information%20and%20consolidate%20their%20anti-Muslim%20Hindu%20vote%20bank.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20issue%20cannot%20be%20spoken%20of%20in%20a%20vacuum.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20words%20and%20actions%20of%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20have%20to%20be%20factored.%20It%20is%20disingenuous%20for%20political%20commentators%20to%20demand%20that%20non-BJP%20aligned%20political%20parties%20and%20citizens%20must%20respond%20to%20this%20proposal%20with%20good%20faith.%20Muslims%20and%20Dalits%20have%20been%20attacked%20over%20the%20past%20nine%20years%2C%20not%20just%20by%20vigilante%20groups%20but%20also%20by%20the%20state%20itself%20through%20the%20promulgation%20of%20anti-conversion%20laws%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20protecting%20Hindus%20from%20%E2%80%98love%20jihad%E2%80%99.%20This%20fear%20mongering%20has%20led%20to%20an%20increasing%20number%20of%20assaults%20against%20Muslims.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%2C%20the%20government%20passed%20an%20ordinance%20and%20then%20the%20parliament%20passed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Funion-cabinet-clears-fresh-bill-to-ban-instant-triple-talaq%2Farticle27888984.ece%5C%22%3Ea%20Bill%20declaring%20triple%20talaq%20as%20illegal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20can%20be%20no%20doubt%20that%20this%20was%20a%20much-needed%20move.%20But%2C%20the%20government%20showed%20its%20true%20colours%20by%20criminalising%20the%20offence.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ftriple-talaq-why-just-muslims-lets-criminalise-the-abandonment-of-all-wives%5C%22%3ENo%20Hindu%20can%20be%20jailed%20for%20abandoning%20his%20wife!%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20words%20indicated%20by%20innumerable%20BJP%20politicians%20from%20the%20prime%20minister%20downwards%20only%20further%20the%20obvious%20point%20that%20this%20government%20is%20not%20interested%20in%20equality%20of%20any%20sort.%20Every%20step%20taken%20is%20to%20demonstrate%20to%20their%20faithful%20that%20they%20will%20put%20Muslims%20in%20their%20place.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EQuite%20glaring%20is%20also%20the%20contradiction%20at%20display%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20government%20on%20one%20side%20pushes%20for%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20in%20the%20name%20of%20ensuring%20equal%20rights%20to%20all%20citizens%20and%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Funion-government-opposes-same-sex-marriages-in-supreme-court%5C%22%3Eopposes%20same-sex%20marriage%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202017%2C%20a%20group%20of%20us%20including%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBezwada%20Wilson%2C%20lawyer%20Dushyant%2C%20actor%20Gul%20Panag%2C%20academic-author%20Mukul%20Kesavan%2C%20author%20Nilanjana%20Roy%2C%20scholar%20S.%20Irfan%20Habib%2C%20and%20Major%20General%20S.%20Vombetkere%20(Retd.)%20presented%20a%20proposal%20to%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Law%20Commission%20Justice%20B.S.%20Chauhan%20who%20had%20been%20appointed%20to%20look%20into%20this%20matter.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20proposed%20legalising%20marriages%20between%20individuals%20of%20various%20genders%20and%20sexual%20orientations%2C%20giving%20them%20all%20the%20same%20rights%20in%20adoption%2C%20similar%20procedures%20with%20regard%20to%20divorce%2C%20succession%20and%20inheritance%20rights.%20We%20also%20proposed%20the%20legitimising%20of%20partnerships%20between%20individuals.%20Identities%20such%20religion%2C%20gender%20and%20sexual%20orientation%20that%20distinguish%20one%20citizen%20from%20another%20were%20removed%20from%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20Civil%20Code.%20Everyone%20campaigning%20for%20an%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20has%20been%20harping%20on%20the%20gender%20bias%20in%20all%20religion-based%20civil%20codes.%20But%20with%20all%20the%20learning%20we%20have%20today%20with%20regard%20to%20gender%2C%20sex%20and%20sexuality%2C%20these%20votaries%20will%20have%20to%20move%20beyond%20their%20binary%20vision%20of%20gender.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20deeper%20philosophical%20problem%20with%20the%20way%20this%20discussion%20has%20been%20framed.%20The%20implied%20meaning%20in%20the%20repeated%20use%20of%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98uniform%20%E2%80%98is%20that%20at%20present%20there%20is%20disorder.%20The%20stress%20is%20on%20uniformity%2C%20because%20that%2C%20it%20is%20said%20will%20bring%20about%20discipline!%20The%20presumption%20here%20is%20that%20uniformity%20ensures%20equality.%20In%20our%20subconscious%20mind%2C%20uniformity%20registers%20as%20a%20synonym%20of%20equality.%20But%2C%20uniformity%20only%20means%20the%20same%20rules%20will%20be%20applicable%20to%20all.%20The%20nature%20of%20the%20change%20is%20not%20central%20to%20the%20contemplation.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20could%20then%20have%20a%20legislation%20that%20is%20discriminative%20in%20its%20intention%20and%2C%20though%20applicable%20to%20all%2C%20unequal%2C%20privileging%20a%20section%20and%20disempowering%20others.%20We%20need%20to%20secure%20for%20all%20citizens%20freedom%2C%20life%2C%20privacy%2C%20justice%2C%20equality%20and%20dignity.%20We%20must%20move%20towards%20a%20civil%20code%20that%20gives%20every%20citizen%20the%20right%20to%20live%20life%20as%20per%20their%20beliefs%20and%20choices%20with%20their%20head%20held%20high.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F20142928%2FIMG_4542.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F20142928%2FIMG_4542.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F20142928%2FIMG_4542-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F20142928%2FIMG_4542-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-565692%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20word%20needs%20to%20be%20present%20in%20these%20discussions%3A%20equity.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20shift%20will%20bring%20to%20the%20table%20other%20related%20issues.%20The%20asymmetry%20in%20our%20society%20is%20stark.%20The%20lack%20of%20education%2C%20rights%20and%20equality%20among%20so%20many%20have%20to%20be%20factored%20in%20when%20we%20make%20drastic%20changes%20in%20social%20laws.%20Even%20the%20most%20necessary%20ethical%20laws%20can%20turn%20into%20oppressive%20tools%20in%20an%20intrinsically%20feudal%20society.%20There%20is%20very%20little%20effort%20put%20into%20changing%20our%20socio-religious%20mindsets.%20In%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20homes%2C%20schools%2C%20colleges%20and%20communities%20operate%20in%20a%20parallel%20violent%20universe.%20Caste%2C%20gender%2C%20religion%20are%20all%20used%20to%20control%20and%20oppress%20the%20weak.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELaws%20are%20also%20so%20complicated%20and%20difficult%20to%20access%20for%20the%20illiterate%20and%20persecuted.%20A%20person%20from%20a%20small%20town%20is%20unable%20to%20even%20get%20a%20death%20certificate%20with%20ease%20and%20here%20we%20are%20speaking%20of%20complex%20changes%20to%20our%20civil%20codes.%20In%20such%20an%20environment%2C%20even%20progressive%20laws%20will%20be%20discarded%20due%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20social%20evolution%2C%20parochial-ness%20or%20they%20will%20be%20weaponised%20by%20the%20dominant.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Political%20parties%20use%20religion%2C%20caste%2C%20sex%20and%20gender%20to%20abuse%20citizens%2C%20courts%20perpetuate%20discriminative%20norms%2C%20and%20the%20police%20force%20is%20hand%20in%20glove%20with%20the%20dominants.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20however%20progressive%2C%20can%20even%20be%20harmful%20because%20it%20will%20challenge%20the%20power%20of%20the%20socially%20prepotent.%20This%20will%20leave%20the%20minorities%20who%20attempt%20to%20use%20the%20new%20provisions%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20threat%20of%20violence.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20need%20ideals%20such%20as%20rights%2C%20liberties%20and%20justice%20to%20become%20everyday%20conversations.%20This%20can%20then%20bring%20about%20a%20grassroots%20level%20demand%20for%20changes%20in%20our%20civil%20codes.%20Governments%20and%20law%20makers%20must%20create%20a%20social%20environment%20that%20allows%20everyone%20to%20raise%20their%20voice%20fearlessly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20not%20to%20say%20that%20laws%20will%20need%20to%20wait%20for%20society%20to%20change.%20Laws%20can%20come%20first%20and%20nudge%20us%20to%20transform.%20This%20will%20happen%20if%20laws%20are%20framed%20with%20social%20consciousness%20and%20in%20order%20to%20further%20democratic%20spirit.%20But%20to%20create%20a%20more%20enlightened%20society%20we%20do%20not%20need%20a%20uniform%20civil%20code.%20The%20problem%20is%20not%20that%20we%20have%20diverse%20set%20of%20civil%20laws.%C2%A0%20It%20is%20their%20degrees%20of%20restrictiveness%20and%20discrimination.%20Unlike%20what%20is%20being%20portrayed%2C%20bringing%20about%20sameness%20should%20not%20be%20the%20thrust.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20also%20far%20more%20difficult.%20An%20individualised%20approach%20to%20every%20set%20of%20civil%20laws%20will%20be%20more%20sensible%20and%20specific%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20diverse%20country%20such%20as%20India.%20Each%20community%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20any%20such%20move.%20Changes%20cannot%20be%20a%20top-down%20dictum%20forced%20upon%20people%20via%20an%20entry%20in%20our%20constitution.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20a%20participatory%20process%20that%20comes%20from%20within%20the%20concerned%20communities.%20This%20will%20indeed%20be%20consultative%20and%20slower%2C%20but%20the%20nuance%20and%20strength%20it%20will%20gain%20will%20make%20the%20changes%20creative%2C%20robust%20and%20flexible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Ft-m-krishna%5C%22%3ET.M.%20Krishna%