E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F8C37Ps2fDm0%3Fsi%3DI0p80djLqm2WI76y%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20has%20so%20far%20caused%20at%20least%20160%20deaths%20and%20there%20are%20reports%20of%202%2C000%20villages%20being%20burnt%20and%20over%20360%20churches%20either%20being%20burnt%20or%20destroyed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELt%20General%20Nair%20spoke%20of%20the%20multiple%20challenges%20that%20the%20armed%20forces%20were%20facing%20in%20the%20state%20that%20has%20been%20marred%20by%20very%20serious%20violence%20since%20May%203.%20Lt%20General%20Nair%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20number%20of%20weapons%E2%80%9D%20with%20civilians%20was%20a%20key%20concern.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20society%20has%20become%20weaponised.%20Unless%20these%20weapons%20come%20back%20in%20whatever%20way%20they%20can%2C%20this%20challenge%20will%20be%20the%20biggest.%20Today%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20so%20much%20against%20each%20other%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20so%20corrupted.%20This%20needs%20to%20be%20stalled%2C%E2%80%9D%20were%20his%20exact%20words.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-looted-weaponry-yet-to-return-to-police-armouries-cm-appeals-afresh-for-surrender%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20how%20various%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eestimates%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20put%20the%20weapons%20%E2%80%9Clooted%E2%80%9D%20from%20police%20armouries%20at%20more%20than%203%2C000.%20On%20June%203%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2F140-weapons-surrendered-manipur-amit-shah-8642463%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20as%20many%20as%204%2C000%20weapons%20had%20been%20looted%20from%20the%20police%20and%20state%20armoury.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20till%20then%20only%20650%20weapons%20had%20been%20recovered.%20The%20kind%20of%20weapons%20%E2%80%9Clooted%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20grave%20concern.%20FIRs%20seen%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20indicate%20the%20loot%20of%20sophisticated%20weapons%20like%20AK%20and%20INSAS%20rifles%2C%20and%20bombs%2C%20among%20others.%20Looters%20also%20took%20away%20bulletproof%20jackets%20and%20set%20fire%20to%20police%20stations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%20is%20meant%20to%20enjoy%20an%20advantage%20as%20per%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdouble-engine%E2%80%9D%20government%2C%20with%20the%20same%20party%20in%20control%20in%20Imphal%20and%20in%20Delhi.%20But%20despite%20a%20long%20and%20unprecedented%20visit%20and%20stay%20by%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20the%20violence%20is%20not%20under%20control.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20last%20month%2C%20upon%20summoning%20the%20chief%20secretary%20of%20the%20state%20had%20remarked%2C%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fbreakdown-of-law-order-supreme-court-manipur-video-case-8871282%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eno%20law%20and%20order%20left%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20role%20of%20the%20state%20police%2C%20whether%20in%20controlling%20violence%20or%20in%20allowing%20the%20%E2%80%9Clooting%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20armouries%2C%20has%20been%20pointed%20out%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20cases%20of%20violence%20have%20been%20shifted%20out%20of%20the%20state%20to%20courts%20in%20Assam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20fresh%20violence%20has%20killed%20at%20least%20eight%20persons%20in%20the%20districts%20of%20Bishnupur%20and%20Churachandpur%20over%20the%20last%20three%20days%20with%20firing%20and%20violence%20continuing%20since%20August%2029.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20little%20coordination%20between%20central%20forces%20and%20those%20from%20the%20state.%20Assam%20Rifles%20has%20been%20locked%20in%20another%20unprecedented%20conflict%20with%20the%20state%20police.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-police-files-fir-against-assam-rifles-for-allowing-kuki-militants-to-flee%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%20Police%20filed%20an%20FIR%20against%20Assam%20Rifles%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20last%20month%20for%20%E2%80%9Callowing%20Kuki%20Militants%20to%20flee%E2%80%9D.%20A%20video%20of%20a%20heated%20exchange%20between%20Assam%20Rifles%20and%20Bishnupur%20police%20had%20earlier%20gone%20viral.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAssam%20Rifles%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fopinion%2Fdangerous-wedge-the-assam-rifles-humiliation-in-manipur%2Fcid%2F1961116%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eadministratively%20under%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20but%20operationally%20works%20under%20the%20army.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20It%20is%20commanded%20by%20army%20officers%2C%20who%20constitute%20around%2080%25%20of%20the%20officer%20cadre.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693638608000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F02122538%2FScreenshot-2023-09-02-at-12.25.06-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fassam-rifles-dg-manipur-situation-unprecedented%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lt%20General%20P.C.%20Nair%20flagged%20the%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20number%20of%20weapons%E2%80%9D%20with%20civilians%20as%20a%20key%20concern.%20He%20also%20said%20society%20%E2%80%9Chas%20become%20weaponised%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fse