threatening%20to%20become%20the%20single-most%20important%20factor%20fuelling%20anti-incumbency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECiting%20a%20senior%20government%20official%2C%20Reuters%20reported%20how%20measures%20by%20a%20government%20in%20a%20panic%20to%20somehow%20alleviate%20price%20rise%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findias-food-price-surge-forces-government-measures-improve-supplies-2023-08-25%2F%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Ccould%20cumulatively%20cost%20the%20government%20over%20%2412%20billion%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAhead%20of%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%20scheme%20was%20spun%20as%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20answer%20to%20the%20UPA%E2%80%99s%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Scheme.%20Analysts%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FPolitics%2FYGfPl6znE7rhdwMC7DGIlM%2FHow-Ujjwala-Yojana-is-emerging-as-Modi-govts-MGNREGS-ahead.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrote%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CMGNREGS%20helped%20UPA%20come%20back%20to%20power%20in%202009%20mirroring%20that%20narrative%20now%20being%20woven%20around%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%20by%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20led%20by%20PM%20Narendra%20Modi%20himself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pmuy.gov.in%2Fabout.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eobjective%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eof%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20scheme%20was%20%E2%80%9Cto%20make%20clean%20cooking%20fuel%20such%20as%20LPG%20available%20to%20the%20rural%20and%20deprived%20households%20which%20were%20otherwise%20using%20traditional%20cooking%20fuels%20such%20as%20firewood%2C%20coal%2C%20cow-dung%20cakes%20etc.%20Usage%20of%20traditional%20cooking%20fuels%20had%20detrimental%20impacts%20on%20the%20health%20of%20rural%20women%20as%20well%20as%20on%20the%20environment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOften%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-bjps-stock-is-falling-and-it-shows%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eparty%20of%20the%20rich%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20BJP%20counted%20on%20the%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%20scheme%20to%20reshape%20its%20own%20and%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20profile.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EComing%20home%20to%20bite%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20this%20flagship%20scheme%20and%20the%20rising%20prices%20of%20LPG%20cylinders%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20burning%20poll%20issue%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPoll%20bound%20states%20like%20Rajasthan%20ruled%20by%20the%20opposition%20Congress%20are%20already%20providing%20LPG%20cylinders%20for%20Rs%20500.%20The%20rising%20prices%20of%20the%20cylinders%20was%20a%20big%20factor%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%20Karnataka%20elections%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20trounced%20the%20BJP%2C%20despite%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20personal%20attention%20and%20focussed%20campaign%20for%20weeks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20provide%20LPG%20cylinders%20at%20Rs%20500%20if%20voted%20to%20power%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20states%20going%20to%20the%20polls%20later%20this%20year%20include%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Telangana.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fdata%2Fdata-the-cost-of-meals-rose-by-65-percent-in-five-years-but-wages-by-just-37-percent%2Farticle67251257.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ethe%20cost%20of%20preparing%20meals%20at%20home%20rose%20by%2065%25%20in%20five%20years%2C%20but%20wages%20by%20just%2028%25-37%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFood%20was%20becoming%20increasingly%20unaffordable%2C%20more%20families%20are%20eating%20unbalanced%20or%20unfulfilling%20meals%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELPG%20cylinders%20being%20unaffordable%2C%20from%20a%20%E2%80%98poll-winner%E2%80%99%20are%20threatening%20to%20become%20a%20noose%20around%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20neck.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOpposition%3A%20%E2%80%9CModi%20acting%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20losing%20power%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20accused%20the%20BJP%20government%20of%20acting%20on%20the%20high%20LPG%20prices%20too%20late%20and%20pegged%20it%20as%20a%20move%20born%20out%20of%20electoral%20expediency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETaking%20aim%20at%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CRakhi%20gift%E2%80%9D%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99%20national%20spokesperson%20Gourav%20Vallabh%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%209%20Rakhis%20before%20this%2C%20based%20on%20that%20there%20should%20be%20Rs%201800%20cut.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20Rakhi%20gift%2C%20this%20is%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekursi%20bachao%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20cut.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20can%20be%20given%20for%20Rs%20400%20you%20have%20increased%20that%20by%20Rs%20700%20and%20given%20it%20for%20Rs%201100.%20And%20now%20you%20are%20saying%20Rs%20200%20cut.%20Is%20this%20a%20gift%20or%20torture%20to%20middle%20income%20families%20and%20women%3F%20This%20is%20not%20a%20gift%2C%20this%20is%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20fear%20of%20losing%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CModiji%20should%20take%20tuition%20from%20Ashok%20Gehlot.%20In%20Rajasthan%2074%20lakh%20BPL%20families%20are%20getting%20cylinders%20for%20Rs%20500%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3ESushmita%20Dev%2C%20TMC%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20is%20%E2%80%9Ctoo%20little%20too%20late.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20does%20not%20justify%20the%20kind%20of%20increment%20that%20the%20LPG%20gas%20cylinders%20saw%20over%20the%20last%204%20and%20a%20half%20years.%20A%20gas%20cylinder%20impacts%20the%20common%20man%E2%80%99s%20household%20budget.%20At%20this%20stage%20to%20decrease%20it%20by%20Rs%20200%20is%20insensitive.%20In%202014%20a%20gas%20cylinder%20was%20Rs%20400%20now%20it%20is%20anything%20between%20Rs%201100-1200.%20I%20think%20it%20is%20too%20little%20and%20too%20late.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20added%20that%20while%20BJP%20did%20win%20the%20Gujarat%20elections%2C%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20they%20lost%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%20was%20because%20%E2%80%9Cprice%20rise%20was%20a%20big%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20economic%20justification%20for%20this%20(price%20cut)%2C%20nor%20have%20international%20gas%20prices%20changed.%20The%20only%20thing%20that%20has%20changed%20is%20that%20there%20are%20four%20state%20elections.%20The%20impetus%20for%20this%20is%20electoral%20mileage%20and%20nothing%20more.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20MP%2C%20the%20move%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20relief%20to%20the%20common%20man.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echunavi%20chaturaee%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eelectoral%20astuteness).%20Whenever%20elections%20are%20around%20the%20corner%2C%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20prices%20are%20slashed%2C%20LPG%20prices%20are%20decreased%20and%20once%20elections%20are%20over%2C%20the%20prices%20are%20increased%20again.%20This%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20relief%20to%20consumers%20in%20any%20way.%20This%20is%20mere%20electoral%20astuteness%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20also%20said%20that%20while%20issues%20like%20price%20rise%20and%20unemployment%20remain%20on%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20agenda%2C%20with%20the%20third%20meeting%20underway%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20such%20moves%20cannot%20be%20used%20as%20diversionary%20tactics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSubsidised%20or%20non-subsidised%20the%20question%20is%20how%20much%20is%20the%20common%20man%20paying.%20You%20are%20writing%20off%20loans%20of%20over%20Rs%2011%20lakh%20crore%20for%20your%20billionaire%20friends%20and%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20common%20man%20you%20make%20distinctions%20between%20subsidised%20and%20non%20subsidised.%20The%20question%20remains%20how%20much%20is%20the%20common%20man%20paying%20out%20of%20his%20pocket.%20And%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20in%20three%20years%20prices%20have%20increased%20by%20over%20Rs%20500%20for%20LPG%20cylinders.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ED%20Raja%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(CPI)%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20move%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Cattempt%20to%20hoodwink%20people%20at%20the%20time%20of%20elections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20looted%20the%20people%20by%20increasing%20the%20price%20of%20LPG%20cylinders%20as%20they%20liked%20now%20they%20have%20decreased%20by%20Rs%20200.%20It%20is%20not%20only%20too%20late%20but%20also%20too%20little.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBJP%3A%20Further%20price%20increase%20depends%20on%20global%20fuel%20prices%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20R.P.%20Singh%2C%20national%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20BJP%20said%20that%20the%20move%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20elections%20and%20is%20a%20bid%20to%20%E2%80%9Ctake%20care%20of%20the%20poor.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20to%20take%20care%20of%20the%20poor.%20This%20will%20benefit%20almost%2011%20crore%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%20scheme.%20What%20is%20wrong%20in%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20people%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20their%20health%20as%20this%20benefits%20women%E2%80%99s%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20being%20asked%20whether%20the%20price%20cut%20was%20too%20little%2C%20Singh%20said%20that%20the%20prices%20need%20to%20be%20compared%20with%20the%20UPA%20regime.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20average%20price%20of%20the%20UPA%20regime%20was%20Rs%20900%20plus%2C%20last%20five%20years%20combined.%20Our%20average%20price%20is%20Rs%20750%20five%20years%20put%20together.%20Now%20the%20prices%20will%20be%20less%20than%20the%20UPA%20regime.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20said%20that%20any%20further%20decrease%20in%20prices%20will%20depend%20on%20the%20international%20fuel%20prices.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20has%20stated%20in%20parliament%20replies%20that%20India%20imports%20over%2060%25%20of%20its%20domestic%20LPG%20consumption.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693621801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FModi-LPG.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flpg-price-cut-modis-rakhi-gift-ends-up-drawing-attention-to-inflation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20Modi%20government%20rushes%20to%20salvage%20its%20flagship%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%20Scheme%2C%20Rs%20200%20is%20a%20small%20fraction%20of%20the%20price%20increase%20of%20the%20last%20three%20years.%20The%20government%20had%20slashed%20subsidy%20on%20LPG%20to%20one-sixth%20since%202018-19.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flpg-price-cut-modis-rakhi-gift-ends-up-drawing-attention-to-inflation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Hate%20Fills%20Every%20Corner%2C%20From%20Classroom%20to%20Prayer%20Room%2C%20Where%20Do%20You%20Look%20for%20Hope%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01162813%2FIMG_2641.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20was%201975%2C%20a%20Holi%20that%20remains%20etched%20in%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20memory.%20For%20several%20years%20leading%20up%20to%20that%20moment%2C%20he%20had%20been%20longing%20for%20a%C2%A0%20particular%20special%20%3Cem%3Epichkari%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20symbol%20of%20extravagance%20in%20those%20days.%20Bright%20and%20colourful%2C%20those%20pichkaris%20would%20dangle%20outside%20shops%2C%20teasing%20those%20who%20passed%20by%2C%20for%20weeks%20before%20Holi.%20When%20asked%2C%20the%20shopkeeper%20said%20it%20would%20cost%20Rs%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20managed%20to%20set%20aside%20around%20Rs%202%20through%20a%20combination%20of%20personal%20savings%20and%20a%20modest%20loan%20from%20a%20friend%2C%20my%20father%20still%20found%20himself%20Rs%205%20short.%20He%20told%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9CAround%20a%20week%20before%20Holi%2C%20I%20had%20gone%20to%20play%20with%20my%20friend%20Arif.%20In%20a%20joint%20family%20with%20his%20father%20and%20uncles%20being%20vegetable%20sellers%2C%20they%20used%20to%20live%20in%20what%20could%20loosely%20be%20described%20as%20a%20Muslim%20ghetto.%E2%80%9D%20He%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20us%20were%20very%20excited%20about%20Holi.%20I%20remember%20telling%20Arif%20that%20this%20Holi%2C%20all%20I%20desired%20was%20that%20coveted%20pichkari%2C%20but%20I%20was%20still%20short%20of%20money.%20Arif%20tried%20to%20reason%20with%20me%20that%20it%20was%20too%20expensive%20and%20we%20could%20even%20play%20without%20a%20pichkari.%20But%20I%20was%20adamant.%20We%20talked%20and%20had%20lunch%20together%20at%20his%20place.%20Then%20I%20left.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20father%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CAround%20two%20days%20before%20Holi%2C%20Arif%20came%20running%20to%20my%20house%20and%20whistled%20to%20call%20me%20outside.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Let%E2%80%99s%20go%20and%20buy%20that%20stupid%20pichkari%20for%20you.%E2%80%99%20I%20reminded%20him%20that%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20money.%20In%20response%2C%20he%20tapped%20his%20pocket%20which%20was%20clinking%20with%20coins.%20He%20gave%20me%20a%20peek%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20filled%20with%20Re%201%2C%2050%20paisa%20and%2025%20paisa%20coins.%20Puzzled%2C%20I%20asked%20where%20he%20got%20the%20money%20from.%20Arif%20replied%20that%20he%20took%20it%20from%20his%20grandmother%2C%20and%20dragged%20me%20to%20the%20shop%20where%20we%20bought%20the%20pichkari.%20Afterwards%2C%20I%20asked%20him%20again%2C%20%E2%80%9CDid%20your%20grandma%20just%20give%20the%20money%20to%20you%3F%20Wow.%E2%80%9D%20It%20was%20then%20that%20Arif%20revealed%2C%20%E2%80%98No.%20She%20has%20a%20%3Cem%3Epotli%3C%2Fem%3E%20where%20she%20keeps%20loose%20change.%20She%20has%20been%20saving%20it%20for%20%3Cem%3Ezakat%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20her%20Hajj%20pilgrimage.%20I%20stole%20it%20from%20there.%E2%80%9D%20Brimming%20with%20emotions%2C%20I%20asked%20him%2C%20%E2%80%98Won%E2%80%99t%20Allah%20be%20angry%20with%20you%3F%E2%80%99%20To%20this%2C%20he%20winked%20and%20said%20He%20would%20understand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20story%20is%20from%20Lucknow%2C%20around%20600%20km%20from%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20from%20where%20the%20horrifying%20video%20of%20a%20teacher%20asking%20her%20students%20to%20slap%20their%20Muslim%20classmate%20recently%20went%20viral.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20are%20you%20hitting%20him%20so%20lightly%3F%20Hit%20him%20hard%E2%80%A6%20His%20face%20is%20turning%20red.%20Hit%20him%20on%20the%20waist%20instead%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20teacher%20declares.%20And%20there%20he%20is%2C%20made%20to%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20the%20class%2C%20with%20tears%20rolling%20down%20his%20cheeks%2C%20his%20dignity%20shattered%2C%20as%20his%20classmates%20%E2%80%93%20some%20perhaps%20even%20counted%20as%20friends%20%E2%80%93%20are%20commanded%20to%20slap%20him%20%E2%80%98hard%E2%80%99.%20As%20the%20teacher%20hurls%20communal%20abuses%20at%20him%2C%20a%20staff%20member%20records%20the%20whole%20incident%2C%20with%20a%20disturbing%20chuckle%20of%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Other%20Children%2C%20that%20Day%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-other-children-that-day-in-muzaffarnagar%5C%22%3EThe%20Other%20Children%2C%20that%20Day%20in%20Muzaffarnagar%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Muslim%20child%20mumbled%20when%20surrounded%20by%20a%20herd%20of%20media%20microphones%2C%20asking%20him%20why%20Tripta%20Tyagi%20%E2%80%93%20his%20teacher%20%E2%80%93%20made%20his%20classmates%20beat%20him.%20Underneath%20the%20superficial%20reason%20%E2%80%93%20he%20got%20a%20multiplication%20table%20wrong%20%E2%80%93%20I%20believe%20he%20knew%20why%20he%20was%20subjected%20to%20the%20abuse.%20Somewhere%20in%20his%20little%20heart%2C%20he%20knows%20it%20was%20a%20hate%20crime.%20And%20this%20knowing%20stings%20too%20deeply%20to%20be%20put%20into%20words.%20Perhaps%20every%20Muslim%20child%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%20has%20been%20forced%20into%20the%20awareness%20of%20being%20a%20religious%20minority.%20Howsoever%20ignorant%20to%20the%20politics%20and%20its%20jargon%2C%20those%20young%20hearts%20sense%20the%20perils%20that%20shadow%20their%20identity.%20The%20assaults%20that%20befall%20their%20existence.%20We%20know%20that%20age%20is%20no%20insulation%20from%20hate%20crime%2C%20when%20Bilkis%20Bano%E2%80%99s%20three-year-old%20daughter%20can%20be%20smashed%20to%20death%20on%20a%20rock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisturbing%20to%20the%20core%2C%20but%20the%20scene%20within%20those%20walls%20of%20Neha%20Public%20School%20is%20merely%20an%20enactment%20%E2%80%93%20a%20fragment%20of%20the%20larger%20theatre%20of%20hatred.%20The%20classroom%20is%20but%20a%20stage%3B%20and%20behind%20the%20curtains%20lie%20the%20writing%20and%20direction%20of%20a%20bigger%2C%20much%20more%20sinister%20script.%20The%20viral%20video%2C%20capturing%20solely%20those%20classmates%20called%20upon%20to%20strike%20the%20Muslim%20boy%2C%20conceals%20a%20much%20longer%20queue%20hidden%20behind%20the%20drapes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20forefront%20of%20this%20line%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20media.%20TV%20anchors%20scream%20their%20veins%20out%20to%20broadcast%20hatred%20and%20feast%20upon%20the%20conscience%20of%20their%20audience%2C%20pushing%20them%20to%20be%20haters%2C%20bigots%20and%20lynch%20mobs.%20They%20fabricate%2C%20label%20and%20locate%20an%20imaginary%20enemy%20needed%20for%20every%20majoritarian%20regime%20(for%20India%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Muslims)%20and%20then%2C%20incite%20the%20public%20to%20not%20just%20despise%20it%20but%20to%20go%20ahead%20and%20annihilate%20this%20enemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20is%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20public%20that%20has%20metamorphosed%20into%20hungry%20mobs%20cooking%2C%20relishing%20and%20savouring%20the%20hatred%20for%20Muslims.%20They%20participate%20in%20the%20grim%20spectacle%20of%20hate%20%E2%80%93%20ranging%20from%20a%20%E2%80%98subtle%E2%80%99%20exclusion%20of%20not%20allowing%20a%20Muslim%20to%20be%20their%20tenant%20to%20sharing%20an%20Islamophobic%20WhatsApp%20forward%20to%20carrying%20out%20rallies%20and%20raising%20provocative%20slogans%20in%20Muslim%20neighbourhoods%20to%20lynching%20them%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%3Cem%3Egau%20raksha%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20love%20jihad.%20United%20in%20their%20hatred%2C%20these%20hungry%20mobs%20carry%20out%20meetings%20and%20conclaves%20to%20strategise%20their%20genocide.%20And%20in%20this%20process%2C%20they%20receive%20undeterred%20backing%20from%20the%20third%20actor%20in%20our%20queue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%2C%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20law%20enforcement%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20assumed%20the%20role%20of%20genocide-enabler%20agencies.%20Transitioning%20from%20being%20a%20mute%20spectator%20to%20occasionally%20even%20becoming%20complicit%20in%20violent%20acts%20against%20Muslims%2C%20and%20further%20proceeding%20to%20apprehend%20victims%20of%20these%20grievous%20offenses%20while%20allowing%20the%20culprits%20to%20evade%20consequences%20%E2%80%93%20the%20recurrence%20of%20such%20events%20has%20cast%20a%20shadow%20of%20doubt%20upon%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20police%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20fourth%20in%20this%20chain%20is%20the%20judiciary%2C%20an%20institution%20entrusted%20with%20the%20duty%20of%20safeguarding%20minority%20rights.%20But%20when%20a%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fmaya-kodnani-cleared-in-second-2002-gujarat-riots-case-8567706%2F%5C%22%3Eoverturns%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20conviction%20of%20BJP%20leader%20Maya%20Kodnani%20her%20involvement%20in%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20pogrom%3B%20when%20Hindutva%20hardliner%20Babu%20Bajrangi%20who%20boasted%20of%20ripping%20out%20the%20womb%20of%20a%20pregnant%20Muslim%20woman%20and%20dragging%20the%20foetus%20with%20a%20sword%20receives%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fahmedabad%2Fbabu-bajrangi-who-made-admissions-in-sting-op-acquitted-8567936%2F%5C%22%3Ereduction%20in%20his%20sentence%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20when%20a%20special%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2019%2F3%2F20%2Fsamjhauta-express-blast-case-court-acquits-four-accused%5C%22%3Eexonerates%3C%2Fa%3E%20all