t-integral-to-islam-says-karnataka-high-court%2F873548%2F%5C%22%3Ecourt%20pronouncing%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20headscarf%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20integral%E2%80%9D%20to%20Islam%20considering%20the%20prohibition%20on%20Muslim%20girls%20wearing%20hijabs%20to%20schools%2C%20the%20list%20is%20long%20and%20it%20raises%20serious%20questions%20whether%20the%20judiciary%20has%20transformed%20into%20a%20tool%20wielded%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%20A%20series%20of%20anti-Muslim%20verdicts%20have%20underscored%20its%20alignment%20with%20the%20Hindutva%20ideology%20and%20its%20failure%20to%20safeguard%20the%20rights%20of%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20in%20the%20queue%20to%20slap%20the%20little%20boy%20stands%20the%20indifferent%20populace%20%E2%80%93%20the%20silent%20chorus%20of%20the%20disinterested%20who%20have%20made%20the%20conscious%20choice%20to%20look%20away%20from%20the%20prevailing%20oppression%2C%20hence%20enabling%20the%20oppressors.%20It%20brings%20to%20mind%20words%20from%20Dante%E2%80%99s%20Inferno%2C%20echoing%20through%20the%20corridors%20of%20time%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EThe%20hottest%20places%20in%20Hell%20are%20reserved%20for%20those%20who%20in%20times%20of%20moral%20crisis%20preserve%20their%20neutrality.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Beyond%20the%20convoluted%20realms%20of%20political%2C%20social%20and%20economic%20turmoil%2C%20our%20society%20finds%20itself%20standing%20in%20a%20moral%20crisis%20today%2C%20when%20our%20shared%20moral%20compass%20seems%20to%20have%20lost%20its%20direction%2C%20obscured%20by%20a%20haze%20of%20indifference.%C2%A0%20As%20some%20among%20us%20look%20away%2C%20refusing%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20shadows%20that%20loom%2C%20and%20as%20silence%20surrounds%20us%20like%20a%20shroud%2C%20we%20are%20inadvertently%20marking%20our%20stance%20in%20the%20annals%20of%20history%2C%20which%20the%20future%20generations%20will%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ghosts%20from%20Nazi%20Germany%20%E2%80%93%20where%2C%20during%20lessons%20on%20%E2%80%98racial%20impurity%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20Jewish%20students%20were%20picked%20out%20to%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20the%20class%20whilst%20teachers%20pointed%20to%20their%20eyes%2C%20ears%2C%20nose%2C%20mouth%20and%20hair%2C%20comparing%20these%20to%20characteristics%20on%20Nazi%20propaganda%20sheets%20%E2%80%93%20have%20come%20to%20haunt%20us.%20After%20the%20Muzaffarnagar%20incident%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffxdurandy%2Fstatus%2F1695139885609263225%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Echilling%20photograph%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%201930s%20resurfaced%20where%20two%20Jewish%20boys%20can%20be%20seen%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20the%20class%2C%20being%20humiliated%2C%20while%20the%20blackboard%20behind%20them%20reads%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20Jew%20is%20our%20biggest%20enemy.%20Beware%20of%20the%20Jew.%E2%80%99%20It%20is%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20parents%20of%20all%20the%20non-Jewish%20students%20in%20that%20classroom%20which%20must%20have%20echoed%20through%20the%20corridors%20of%20history%20as%20their%20children%20were%20stripped%20of%20humanity.%20And%20it%20is%20the%20same%20ghosts%20of%20silence%20that%20have%20come%20back%20to%20haunt%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20will%20the%20silences%20of%20the%20parents%20of%20all%20non-Muslim%20students%20who%20were%20asked%20to%20slap%20their%20friend%2C%20or%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20classmates%20of%20Arnazbanu%2C%20the%20Class%2010%20topper%20of%20Shri%20K.%20T.%20Patel%20Smriti%20Vidyalaya%20in%20Gujarat%20who%20returned%20home%20in%20tears%20after%20the%20school%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmuslim-girl-topper-denied-award-gujarat-school-religious-discrimination%5C%22%3Erefused%20to%20honour%20her%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20awarding%20all%20other%20toppers.%20In%20dark%20times%20like%20these%2C%20such%20silences%20are%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETime%20stands%20as%20a%20relentless%20recorder%20of%20the%20sins%20of%20these%20silences.%20An%20unforgiving%20chronicle%2C%20it%20carries%20the%20weight%20of%20remembrance%20for%20those%20who%20looked%20away%20when%20Anne%20Frank%20and%20her%20friends%20murdered.%20In%20Hannah%20Goslar%E2%80%99s%20poignant%20memoir%2C%20%3Cem%3EMy%20Friend%20Anne%20Frank%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20another%20tale%20is%20told%20%E2%80%93%20that%20of%20Lucie%2C%20a%20once-dear%20friend%20who%20would%20later%20join%20the%20Nazi%20youth%20group%2C%20severing%20her%20friendship%20with%20Jew%20children%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CAnne%20and%20I%20were%20shocked%20to%20know%20that%20Lucie%E2%80%99s%20parents%20had%20joined%20the%20Dutch%20Nazi%20party%2C%20the%20NSB.%20Lucie%20had%20stopped%20inviting%20us%20to%20her%20birthday%20parties%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20now%20we%20understood%20why%E2%80%A6%20We%20found%20out%20later%20that%20Lucie%20joined%20for%20a%20time%20the%20Jeugdstorm%2C%20the%20Nazi%20youth%20group%2C%20the%20name%20of%20which%20meant%20%E2%80%98Youth%20Storm%E2%80%99.%20I%20saw%20her%20once%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20in%20uniform%3A%20knee-length%20belted%20black%20skirt%2C%20red-topped%20black%20cap%2C%20long-sleeved%20sky-blue%20button-down%20shirt.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20tell%20if%20she%20saw%20me%20but%20I%20hurried%20on%2C%20not%20stopping%20to%20say%20hello.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20Neha%20Public%20School%20not%20been%20sealed%20and%20the%20young%20Muslim%20boy%E2%80%99s%20best%20friend%20had%20gone%20back%20to%20class%20the%20next%20day%20only%20to%20find%20his%20friend%E2%80%99s%20seat%20empty%2C%20what%20thoughts%20would%20cross%20his%20mind%3F%20At%20a%20very%20young%20age%2C%20he%20would%20have%20learnt%20the%20power%20of%20hate.%20Goslar%E2%80%99s%20words%20point%20to%20a%20similar%20ache%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EThat%20first%20day%20of%20school%20when%20I%20came%20in%20to%20see%20Anne%E2%80%99s%20seat%20was%20empty%2C%20I%20felt%20as%20if%20a%20knife%20had%20grazed%20my%20heart.%20Several%20other%20seats%20were%20also%20empty%E2%80%A6%20Every%20day%20it%20seemed%20there%20were%20more%20students%20missing.%20We%20never%20knew%20if%20an%20absent%20student%20that%20day%20meant%20they%20were%20simply%20sick%20or%20if%20yet%20another%20family%20had%20been%20deported%20or%20if%20that%20friend%20had%20gone%20into%20hiding.%20I%20felt%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20keep%20up%20morale%20when%20I%20never%20knew%20what%20awaited%20us%20when%20we%20got%20to%20our%20classroom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20come%20across%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Findore-child-stripped-religious-slogans-madhya-pradesh-booked-minors-8555978%2F%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20where%20a%2012-year-old%20Muslim%20boy%20can%20be%20seen%20sobbing%20hard%2C%20gripped%20with%20fear%20as%20three%20minors%20are%20seen%20stripping%20him%20and%20forcing%20him%20to%20chant%20religious%20slogans%20as%20well%20as%20slogans%20like%20%E2%80%98Hindustan%20Zindabad%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Pakistan%20Murdabad%E2%80%99%2C%20we%20cannot%20escape%20being%20huanted%20by%20the%20infamous%20image%20of%201941%20where%20Nazi%20German%20children%20are%20chasing%20a%20wounded%20Jewish%20woman.%20The%20parallels%20between%20these%20two%20unsettling%20moments%20%E2%80%93%20separated%20by%20decades%20and%20distance%20%E2%80%93%20is%20a%20stark%20reminder%20of%20the%20capacity%20of%20hatred%20to%20fuel%20cruelty%2C%20even%20in%20the%20hearts%20of%20the%20young.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20witness%20the%20chilling%20repercussions%20of%20young%20impressionable%20hearts%20being%20marred%20by%20prejudice%20and%20hatred%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20fresh%20buds%20of%20hope%20waiting%20to%20bloom%2C%20a%20few%20dreams%20of%20compassion%20waiting%20to%20soar.%20I%20was%20once%20told%20by%20a%2013-year-old%20girl%20who%20stays%20in%20my%20neighbourhood%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20close%20friends%20with%20a%20Muslim%20boy%20in%20our%20class.%20One%20day%2C%20when%20my%20friend%E2%80%99s%20mother%20got%20to%20know%2C%20she