E%20The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20arrested%20Jet%20Airways%20founder%20Naresh%20Goyal%20after%20questioning%20him%20on%20Friday%20(September%201)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Findiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fenforcement-directorate-questions-jet-airways-founder-naresh-goyal-rs-538-cr-bank-fraud-2429860-2023-09-01%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20report%20added%20that%20ED%20officials%20took%20Goyal%20in%20for%20questioning%20as%20he%20was%20preparing%20to%20be%20questioned%20by%20the%20Serious%20Fraud%20Investigation%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%2C%20a%20federal%20financial%20crimes%20agency%2C%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnaresh-goyal-ed-takes-up-rs-538-crore-canara-bank-fraud-case-being-probed-by-cbi%5C%22%3Econducted%20searches%20at%20six%20to%20seven%20premises%3C%2Fa%3E%20linked%20to%20Goyal%20in%20July%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20filed%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20against%20him%20and%20others%20based%20on%20a%20previous%20case%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20filed%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoyal%E2%80%99s%20Jet%20Airways%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20defrauding%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20Canara%20Bank%20of%20Rs%20538%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanara%20Bank%20had%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20alleging%20that%20it%20had%20sanctioned%20credit%20limits%20and%20loans%20to%20Jet%20Airways%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%20848.86%20crore%2C%20of%20which%20an%20amount%20of%20Rs%20538.62%20crore%20is%20outstanding%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20complaint%20also%20alleged%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20forensic%20audit%20that%20Goyal%E2%80%99s%20companies%20committed%20%E2%80%9Cglaring%20irregularities%E2%80%9D%20in%20their%20transactions%20with%20the%20bank%2C%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusine