ney%20on%20Instagram%20and%20has%20an%20earnest%20following%20of%2053%2C319%20thousand%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20been%20loving%20our%20journey%20together%20and%20some%20brands%20have%20been%20generous%20enough%20to%20sponsor%20us.%20There%20is%20a%20UP-based%20gentleman%20who%20sponsored%20Buttercup%E2%80%99s%20food%20for%20the%20Chardham%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20childhood%20we%20have%20all%20heard%20our%20fathers%20and%20grandfathers%20brag%20and%20say%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eduniya%20dekhi%20hai%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E(I%20have%20seen%20the%20world)%2C%20well%2C%20with%20such%20diversity%20in%20India%2C%20they%20might%20have%20just%20peeked%20through%20the%20keyhole%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20door.%20However%2C%20not%20for%20Yati%2C%20as%20he%20and%20Buttercup%20have%20literally%20been%20seeing%20the%20world%2C%20one%20town%20at%20a%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693404383000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-1693402264.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D328577%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Interested%20in%20slow%20travel%20and%20cultures%20across%20India%2C%20Yati%20Gaur%20decided%20to%20walk%20through%20the%20country.%20He%20has%20completed%20five%20walking%20expeditions%20covering%20states%20such%20as%20Goa%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%20with%20his%20rescue%20dog%2C%20Buttercup.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328577%2Fyati-gaur-from-uttar-pradesh-explores-india-on-foot-with-rescue-dog-travel-plans%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'It%20was%20like%20losing%20a%20family%20member'%3A%20The%20US%20soldier%20who%20cried%20afte