agements%2C%20which%20results%20in%20their%20concerns%20not%20being%20addressed%20during%20the%20decision-making%20process.%20On%20average%2C%20more%20than%2050%25%20of%20all%20vulnerable%20communities%20surveyed%20suggested%20that%20improvements%20from%20the%20government%20are%20needed%20in%20terms%20of%20health%2C%20sanitation%2C%20flood%20prevention%20infrastructure%20and%20other%20general%20infrastructure.%20As%20much%20as%2060%25%20of%20the%20population%20takes%20water%20from%20public%20wells%20and%20does%20not%20have%20access%20to%20water%20connections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDense%20concrete%20and%20impermeable%20surfaces%2C%20taking%20the%20place%20of%20natural%20infrastructure%20like%20water%20bodies%2C%20green%20cover%20and%20open%20spaces%2C%20have%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwri-india.org%2Fblog%2Fkerala-flooding-natural-calamity-or-manmade-disaster%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimpacted%20the%20ability%20of%20cities%20to%20manage%20water%20runoff%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20heavy%20and%20erratic%20rainfall%20patterns%2C%20resulting%20in%20devastating%20instances%20of%20flooding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20where%20nature-based%20solutions%20play%20an%20important%20role.%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Kochi%2C%20for%20example%2C%2012%20sites%20that%20are%20prone%20to%20flooding%20and%20dumping%20have%20been%20turned%20into%20urban%20forests%20through%20the%20Kochi%20Municipal%20Corporation%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wri-india.org%2Fblog%2Fkawaki-community-led-tree-based-intervention-climate-resilience-case-study%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKawaki%20initiative.%3C%2Fa%3E%20These%20erstwhile%20mosquito%20breeding%20grounds%20are%20now%20seeing%20the%20scientific%20plantation%20and%20maintenance%20of%20saplings%2C%20which%20as%20fully%20grown%20trees%20will%20offe