co-founders%20Abhay%20Deshpande%2C%20Vikram%20Prabakar%2C%20Abhishek%20Deshpande%2C%20Anirudha%20Jalan%2C%20and%20Ekta%20Narain.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20of%20going%20back%20to%20the%20ecosystem.%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20in%20an%20area%20that%20was%20more%20impactful%20not%20only%20for%20humans%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20but%20also%20the%20environment.%20And%20I%20saw%20waste%20management%20as%20a%20good%20opportunity.%20The%20intent%20was%20to%20disrupt%20the%20informal%20waste%20supply%20chain%20management%20using%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhay%20pointed%20out%20that%20there%20are%20at%20least%20six%20stakeholders%20involved%20in%20the%20unorganised%20waste%20supply%20chain.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20waste%20in%20your%20dustbin%20either%20reaches%20the%20recycler%2C%20the%20landfills%2C%20or%20the%20oceans.%20But%20before%20it%20reaches%20the%20destination%2C%20it%20is%20handled%20by%20at%20least%20six%20people%20like%20ragpickers%2C%20small%20and%20large-scale%20scrap%20dealers%2C%20bailers%2C%20traders%2C%20and%20recyclers.%20It%20is%20a%20very%20complex%20and%20informal%20supply%20chain%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20scrap%20dealers%20are%20not%20educated%20and%20well-connected%20with%20other%20stakeholders.%20They%20only%20know%20one%20person%20above%20and%20one%20person%20below%20their%20supply%20chain.%20We%20connected%20them%20to%20the%20other%20stakeholders%20directly%20to%20bring%20additional%20income%20through%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F180076%2Fbhopal-online-kababdiwala-doorstep-scrap-collection-homes-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonline%20marketplace%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReiterating%20the%20gaps%2C%20co-founder%20Abhishek%20Deshpande%20tells%20%3Cstro