0it%20through%20her%20parents%E2%80%99%20eyes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20the%2042-year-old%20founded%20Yunikee%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20organisation%20dedicated%20to%20helping%20persons%20with%20hearing%20disabilities%20in%20India%20%E2%80%94%20with%20her%20husband%20Chaithanya%20Kothapalli%20(44)%20and%20her%20colleague%20Rahul%20Jain%20(34).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20never%20saw%20my%20parents%20as%20being%20different%20from%20other%20parents%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nita%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20me%2C%20it%20was%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20my%20parents%20not%20being%20able%20to%20hear.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20special%20educator%2C%20Nita%20realised%20the%20inaccessibility%20of%20resources%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F133654%2Fhearing-impaired-transforms-language-tech%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeaf%20children%3C%2Fa%3E%20often%20faced%2C%20a%20realisation%20that%20later%20served%20as%20her%20driving%20force%20to%20co-found%20Yunikee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Chaithanya%2C%20an%20IT%20professional%2C%20it%20was%20watching%20his%20wife%20Nita%E2%80%99s%20work%20ethic%20while%20she%20taught%20deaf%20kids%2C%20which%20had%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20him.%20So%2C%20after%20a%2025-year-long%20stint%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20Chaithanya%20quit%20his%20job%20in%202020%20to%20join%20Nita%20in%20creating%20the%20social%20impact%20platform.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoining%20their%20vision%20was%20Rahul%2C%20an%20ISL%20teacher%20who%20had%20been%20working%20with%20Nita%20since%202017%20teaching%20deaf%20kids%20in%20special%20schools.%20Being%20deaf%2C%20Rahul%20brought%20unique%20insights%20to%20the%20table%20on%20how%20they%20could%20formulate%20a%20platform%20that%20would%20cater%20to%20solving%20some%20vital%20problems%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.t