0we%20provide%20them%20with%20electronic%20devices%2C%20content%2C%20and%20training%20to%20teachers.%20We%20focus%20on%20improving%20the%20performance%20of%20children%20in%20Maths%20and%20Science%20because%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20these%20subject%20teachers%20in%20the%20government%20schools%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fg0HA2PbezIc%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuskaan%20Dreams%20also%20uses%20a%20third%20party%20Tic%20Tac%20Learning%20app%E2%80%99s%20unique%20%E2%80%9Ctic-tac%E2%80%9D%20learning%20module%2C%20wherein%20they%20animate%20pictures%20and%20high-quality%20video%20content%20aligned%20with%20the%20NCERT%20syllabus.%20With%20a%20special%20focus%20on%20subjects%20like%20Science%20and%20Math%2C%20all%20chapters%20and%20exercises%20are%20converted%20into%20animated%20videos%20in%20Hindi.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20chapter%20on%20nutrients%20and%20food%20is%20converted%20into%20an%20animated%20video%20to%20disseminate%20information%20in%20an%20interesting%20and%20engaging%20way%2C%20and%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20story%20to%20help%20students%20retain%20what%20they%20learned%20better.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20followed%20by%20teacher%20training%20and%201-1%20feedback%20and%20support%20to%20teachers%20to%20ensure%20the%20adoption%20of%20technology%20in%20teaching%20practices.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20training%20is%20divided%20into%20four%20modules%20that%20are%20mandatory%20for%20each%20teacher%20to%20attend.%20We%20make%20our%20teachers%20familiar%20with%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20digital%20lesson%2C%20teaching%2C%20and%20learning%20models%20using%20technology%20and%20methods%20of%20delivering%20instruction.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20invest%20in%20teacher%20training%20to%20foster%20a%20stronger%20education%20ecosystem%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20informs%20that%20his%20team%20works%20with%20any%20school%20for%202-3%20years.%20After%20they%20leave%2C%20they%20provide%20virtual%20tech%20support%20to%20ensure%20teachers%20are%20ensuring%20the%20consistency%20of%20digital%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20we%20stop%20hand%20holding%20the%20schools%2C%20we%20try%20to%20build%20capacity%20to%20lower%20dependency%20on%20our%20team%20so%20they%20remain%20efficient%20post-exit.%20Other%20than%20this%2C%20we%20have%20engaged%20private%20organisations%20like%20Pernod%20Ricard%20India%20Foundation%2C%20LTI%20Mindtree%2C%20Yash%20Technologies%2C%20and%20Acuity%20Knowledge%20Partners%20who%20offer%20resources%2C%20expertise%2C%20and%20funding%20to%20support%20the%20sustainability%20of%20our%20initiative%20for%20at%20least%20two%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%981%20Million%20by%202025%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20says%20that%20every%20year%2C%20they%20conduct%20an%20annual%20survey%20to%20understand%20the%20experience%20of%20children%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F105260%2Findia-literacy-project-interactive-learning-rural-government-schools%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20classrooms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1uEv8ngaoPY4ZrB19oQVB6pRnFMv-86TuFXHxKt9R9HY%2Fedit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E95.2%20percent%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20children%20are%20enjoying%20the%20digital%20learning%20experience%20as%20compared%20to%20before%20our%20intervention%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-4-1692363983.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abhishek%20is%20planning%20to%20reach%20out%20to%201%20million%20students%20by%202025.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-4-1692363983.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-4-1692363983-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-4-1692363983-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-4-1692363983-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-4-1692363983-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327626%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAbhishek%20is%20planning%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20one%20million%20students%20by%202025.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20also%20came%20with%20a%20set%20of%20challenges.%20Abhishek%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20biggest%20challenge%20was%20to%20make%20government%20school%20teachers%20in%20their%2040s%20start%20adapting%20technology.%20But%20thankfully%2C%20over%20the%20years%20we%20were%20able%20to%20achieve%20this%20with%20our%20intervention.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20challenge%20to%20ensure%20schools%20continue%20to%20use%20digital%20means%20after%20they%20leave%2C%20he%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CAs%20an%20external%20organisation%2C%20we%20cannot%20guarantee%20the%20school%E2%80%99s%20actions%20once%20our%20direct%20engagement%20comes%20to%20an%20end.%20But%20we%20track%20the%20usage%20and%20effectiveness%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F251330%2Fprabhat-saxena-uttar-pradesh-iit-srijan-ek-soch-ngo-rural-india-education-underprivileged-smart-classes-shiksha-ki-gadi-upliftment-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmart%20TVs%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20digital%20tools%20through%20regular%20evaluations.%20We%20also%20assist%20schools%20with%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20digital%20infrastructure.%20We%20strive%20to%20create%20an%20environment%20where%20smart%20TVs%20and%20digital%20tools%20become%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20school%E2%80%99s%20educational%20practices.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20initiative%2C%20Abhishek%20does%20not%20charge%20any%20fee%20from%20the%20students.%20The%20expenses%20are%20managed%20through%20funds%20from%20CSR%20activities%20and%20corporate%20collaborations%20from%20partners%20like%20Amazon%20India%2C%20Linkedin%2C%20ONGC%2C%20and%20Hindustan%20Zinc.%20To%20further%20the%20cause%2C%20he%20is%20planning%20to%20expand%20the%20project%20to%20Karnataka%20schools%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year%20and%20reach%20out%20to%201%20million%20students%20by%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20big%20goals%20ahead%2C%20Abhishek%20speaks%20about%20the%20decision%20he%20took%20years%20back%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20was%20placed%20in%20any%20company%20like%20my%20friends%2C%20I%20would%20be%20just%20another%20corporate%20employee.%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20I%20took%20a%20stand.%20Whatever%20happened%2C%20happened%20for%20a%20good%20reason.%20Although%20we%20work%2010-12%20hours%20daily%2C%20I%20cherish%20this%20roller%20coaste